"font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 6pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 6pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\"><input type=\"image\" src=\"http://dev.curio.com/public/content/img_contents/1523263618.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"263\"></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 13.3333px;\"><span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">　　仕宏拍賣有</span><span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">限公司謹訂</span><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">在</span><span style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">2017<span lang=\"ZH-TW\">年</span>11<span lang=\"ZH-TW\">月</span>25 - 26<span lang=\"ZH-TW\">日</span></span><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">於</span><span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">香港君悅酒店隆重舉行</span><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">秋</span><span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">季拍賣</span><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">會及預展</span><span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">，四大類別專場</span><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">拍品免費公開展出</span><span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">：<b>古董</b></span><b><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">級</span></b><b><span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">名茶</span></b><span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">﹑<b>茶具．香道．花器</b></span><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">﹑</span><b><span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">養生尚品</span></b><b><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">及珍稀相機</span></b><span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">，</span><span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">呈現多元文化</span><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">收藏</span><span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">的面貌與視野，</span><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">誠</span><span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">邀藏家參與共</span><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">賞</span><span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">至臻藝術。</span><span style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\"></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 13.3333px;\"><span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">　　本次秋拍古董普洱</span><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">專場全數</span><span style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">116</span><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">件茶品總估值超過</span><span style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">3<span lang=\"ZH-HK\">千萬港元。</span></span><span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">亮點以</span><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">「</span><b><span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">普洱印字級一條龍</span></b><b><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">」</span></b><span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">重磅領銜，整組拍品完整收藏</span><span style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">50<span lang=\"ZH-TW\">年代至</span></span>70<span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">年代文革前的十三片印級普洱茶；展示出中國普洱茶的演變進程，了解茶界傳奇的發展，更顯彌足珍貴</span><b></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"font-size: 13.3333px; margin-left: 0in; text-align: justify; text-indent: 21.25pt;\"><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">預展現場設有普洱品鑒會，讓一眾愛茶</span><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">