ground-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">亟待亮相，</span><span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"新細明體\",\"serif\"\'>呈現多元文化</span><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:\n12.0pt;font-family:\"新細明體\",\"serif\";mso-fareast-language:ZH-HK\'>收藏</span><span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"新細明體\",\"serif\"\'>的面貌與視野，</span><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"新細明體\",\"serif\";\nmso-fareast-language:ZH-HK\'>誠</span><span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:\n12.0pt;font-family:\"新細明體\",\"serif\"\'>邀藏家參與共</span><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"新細明體\",\"serif\";mso-fareast-language:\nZH-HK\'>賞</span><span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\n\"新細明體\",\"serif\"\'>至臻藝術。</span><span style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\n\"新細明體\",\"serif\"\'><p></p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"新細明體\",\"serif\"\'>　　本次秋拍古董普洱</span><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:\n12.0pt;font-family:\"新細明體\",\"serif\";mso-fareast-language:ZH-HK\'>專場</span><span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"新細明體\",\"serif\"\'>亮點頗多，以</span><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">「</span><b><span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\'font-family:\"新細明體\",\"serif\";mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\'>普洱印字級一條龍</span></b><b><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\'font-family:\"新細明體\",\"serif\";mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-language:ZH-HK\'>」</span></b><span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"新細明體\",\"serif\"\'>重磅領銜，整組拍品完整收藏</span><span style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"新細明體\",\"serif\"\'>50<span lang=\"ZH-TW\">年代至</span></span>70<span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"新細明體\",\"serif\";\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\'>年代文革前的十三片印級普洱茶；展示出中國普洱茶的演變進程，了解茶界傳奇的發展，更顯彌足珍貴。仕宏拍賣總裁周先生表示「普洱茶承載著深蘊的中國文化，一杯湯色紅釅的茶，可以道出時代更迭的軌跡。我們希望可以通過更多元的收藏選擇，普洱茶﹑沉香﹑茶道具，甚至陳皮﹑花膠來感受過去精益求精的生活態度，讓生活成為藝術收藏的一種，傳承東方文化中雅致的品味。」</span><b><p></p></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:0in;mso-para-margin-left:0gd;\ntext-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:21.25pt;mso-char-indent-count:\n1.77\"><span lang=\"JA\" style=\'font-family:\"新細明體\",\"serif\";mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\'>預展現場設有普洱品鑒會，讓一眾愛茶</span><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\'font-family:\"新細明體\",\"serif\";mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-language:ZH-HK\'>藏</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\'font-family:\"新細明體\",\"serif\";mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\'>友品嘗</span><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\'font-family:\n\"新細明體\",\"serif\";mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-fareast-language:ZH-HK\'>與拍品同批次之</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\'font-family:\n\"新細明體\",\"serif\";mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\'>普洱</span><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\'font-family:\"新細明體\",\"serif\";mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-language:ZH-HK\'>茶</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\'font-family:\"新細明體\",\"serif\";mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\'>；</span><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\'font-family:\n\"新細明體\",\"serif\";mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-fareast-language:ZH-HK\'>費用全免，席次有限，敬請預約。</span><span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\'font-family:\"新細明體\",\"serif\";mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-fareast