mily:arial\"=\"\">　</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\"></span></p><p></p><p></p>					</div>', 'admin', 'admin', '1508860800', '1523262253', null, '1', null, null, '/public/pdf/content/1523005701.pdf', '/public/pdf/content/1523005699.pdf', null), ('4', 'L&H Auction proudly presents The collection of 13 vintage Puer Tea Masterpieces: 1950s -1970s’ at the Hong Kong International Tea Fair', '歷史級陳年普洱系列收藏 「普洱印級茶一條龍」將於香港國際茶展率先展出', '18', '', '<div class=\"pcontent\">\n<p>&nbsp;<b style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;\nfont-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-language:ZH-HK\">L&amp;H Auction proudly presents</span></b></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;mso-line-height-alt:\n12.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;\nfont-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-language:ZH-HK\">The collection of 13 vintage Puer Tea Masterpieces: 1950s -1970s’</span></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;mso-line-height-alt:\n12.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;\nfont-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-language:ZH-HK\">at the&nbsp;Hong Kong&nbsp;International&nbsp;Tea Fair&nbsp;</span></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\nmso-line-height-alt:12.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></b></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"line-height:12.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; At this year\'s Hong Kong&nbsp;International&nbsp;Tea Fair, L&amp;H Auction Co., Ltd (L&amp;H Auction) proudly presents “<b>The collection of 13 vintage Puer Tea Masterpieces: 1950s -1970s’</b>”, one of the highlights for upcoming fall auction.</p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\">“The collection of 13 vintage Puer Tea Masterpieces: 1950s -1970s’”, including 13 pieces of rare puer tea from 1950s to 1970s’ as following: </p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Red Mark Puer Cake (Early Stage), Red Mark Puer Cake (Later Stage),Red Mark Discus Puer Cake, Red Mark Puer Cake<a href=\"http://sunsingtea.com/index.php?route=product/product&amp;product_id=121\"><span style=\"color: windowtext; text-decoration-line: none;\">&nbsp;(without package period)</span></a>, Blue Mark Puer Cake (Grade A), Blue Mark Puer Cake (Grade B), Fu Lu Gong Puer Cake, Sipu Tribute Puer Cake, Green Mark Puer Cake (Large Characters), Green Mark Puer Cake (Small Characters),Round Discus Puer Cake, Green Mark Puer Cake<a href=\"http://sunsingtea.com/index.php?route=product/product&amp;product_id=121\"><span style=\"color: windowtext; text-decoration-line: none;\">&nbsp;(without package period)</span></a> and Yellow Mark Puer Tea.</p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; In 1950s, puer tea production was centralized and run by Yunnan Tea Factories under government in China. With the mass production, there were only 5 products, the Red Mark Puer Cake, the Red Mark Discus Puer Cake, the Blue Mark Puer Cake, and Red Mark Puer Cake<a href=\"http://sunsingtea.com/index.php?route=product/product&amp;product_id=121\"><span style=\"color: windowtext; text-decoration-line: none;\">&nbsp;(without package period)</span></a>. In the early setup of PRC, the puer tea cake production has come to the end due to the political movement.</p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;&nbsp; The historical value of this collection bring the estimated price of “The collection of 13 vintage Puer Tea Masterpieces: 1950s -1970s’” up to 3 millions hong kong dollors.</p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; L&amp;H Auction will also accept consignments at the Tea fair. Tea lovers and collectors are welcomed to bring their rare collections to us for free valuation</p><p></p><p></p>\n<p><img src=\"/public/content/img_contents/1523263916.png\" width=\"712\" height=\"456\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;mso-no-proof:yes\">(High-res photo link) <a href=\"https://www.dropbox.com/s/l6cb5i9s1m49eaf/Dragon.jpg?dl=0\">https://www.dropbox.com/s/l6cb5i9s1m49eaf/Dragon.jpg?dl=0</a></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><br>\n<!--[if !supportLineBreakNewLine]--><br>\n<!--[endif]--></span><span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;mso-no-proof:yes\"></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<div align=\"center\">\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"margin-left:36.9pt;border-collapse:collapse;border:none;mso-border-alt:\n solid windowtext .5pt;mso-yfti-tbllook:1184;mso-padding-alt:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt;\n mso-border-insideh:.5pt solid windowtext;mso-border-insidev:.5pt solid windowtext\">\n    <tbody>\n        <tr>\n            <td width=\"486\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:364.5pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\n  mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt\">\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-language:\n  ZH-HK\">Hong Kong&nbsp;International&nbsp;Tea Fair&nbsp;2017</span></p><p></p><p></p>\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-language:\n  ZH-HK\">Date</span><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\n  mso-ascii-font-family:Cambria;mso-hansi-font-family:Cambria;mso-fareast-language:\n  ZH-HK\">：</span><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\n  mso-fareast-langu