e:13.0pt;font-family:\nSimSun;mso-fareast-font-family:新細明體;mso-fareast-language:ZH-HK\"></span></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\nmso-line-height-alt:12.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></b></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\"font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-language:ZH-HK\">仕宏拍賣有限公司</span>(<span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\"font-family:\n&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-fareast-language:ZH-HK\">仕宏拍賣</span>)<span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\"font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-language:ZH-HK\">將參展由香港貿易發展局主辦之</span>2017<span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\"font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-fareast-language:ZH-HK\">香港國際茶展，並率先於展會中曝光秋季拍賣重量級普洱拍品</span> - <b><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\"font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-language:ZH-HK\">「普洱印級茶一條龍」</span></b><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\"font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-language:ZH-HK\">，與惜茶之友一同欣賞此珍藏極品。</span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\">&nbsp;<span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\"font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-language:ZH-HK\">「普洱印級茶一條龍」</span><b><span style=\"color:#C72B1B\">(</span></b><b><span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\"font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;color:#C72B1B\">估價：</span><span style=\"color:#C72B1B\">HK$ 3,000,000)</span></b><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\"font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-fareast-language:ZH-HK\">匯集<b>十三餅由</b></span><b>50</b><b><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\"font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-language:\nZH-HK\">年代至文化大革命前的印級普洱茶</span></b><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\"font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-language:\nZH-HK\">，</span><span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\"font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">分別以早期紅印、紅印鐵餅、無紙紅印、甲級藍印等舉足輕重的印級普洱圓茶為首，直至七十年代的黃印圓茶止。在文革以前</span><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\"font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-language:ZH-HK\">普洱茶葉均</span><span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\"font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">以古法工序製茶，並以蕎木茶菁為料，屬單一茶菁的生茶茶品，品質甚佳。鑑於年代久遠，品相上佳的印級茶在市場上已經愈見稀少，價格亦每每攀升；以印級茶的始祖紅印圓茶為例，在仕宏拍賣</span>2017<span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\"font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">春季拍賣中，成交價已高達</span>65<span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\"font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri\">萬港元一片，可見茶葉品質和人文歷史意義，使之成為普洱茶中的曠世珍寶。</span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\"font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">「普洱印級茶一條龍」把普洱茶的演變進程同時收納囊中，體現茶葉於中國乃至於世界傳奇的發展，</span><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\"font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-language:ZH-HK\">包含人文歷史等重要無形價值</span><span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\"font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">，更顯彌足珍貴。</span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p><img src=\"/public/content/img_contents/1523263916.png\" width=\"712\" height=\"456\" alt=\"\"><img src=\"\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 12px; text-align: center;\">(High-res photo link)&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.dropbox.com/s/l6cb5i9s1m49eaf/Dragon.jpg?dl=0\" style=\"font-size: 12px; text-align: center;\">https://www.dropbox.com/s/l6cb5i9s1m49eaf/Dragon.jpg?dl=0</a></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\"font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri\">展覽期間仕宏拍賣將於<b>展位</b></span><b>5F E-29</b><span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\"font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri\">進行秋季拍品公開徵集，專家團隊將提供估值服務，與四海藏家增進溝通。上拍後若不成交，絕不收佣金及手續費，歡迎踴躍參與。</span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">徵集項目：古董名茶</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"> | </span><span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\nfont-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri\">茶具花器</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"> | </span><span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">中國書畫</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"> |</span><span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">古董珍玩</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"> | </span><span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">沉香奇楠</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"> |<br>\n<!--[if !supportLineBreakNewLine]--><br>\n<!--[endif]--></span><span style=\"font-size:6.0pt\"></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<div align=\"center\">\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"margin-left:36.9pt;border-collapse:collapse;border:none;mso-border-alt:\n solid windowtext .5pt;mso-yfti-tbllook:1184;mso-padding-alt:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt;\n mso-border-insideh:.5pt solid windowtext;mso-border-insidev:.5pt solid windowtext\">\n    <tbody>\n        <tr>\n            <td width=\"486\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:364.5pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\n  mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt\">\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b><span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\"font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\n  mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">第</span>9</b><b><span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\"font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\n  mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">屆香港國際茶展</span></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\"font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:\n  Calibri;mso-fareast-language:ZH-HK\">日期：</span>2017<span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\"font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:\n  Calibri\">年</span>8<span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\"font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\n  mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">月</span>17 - 19<span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\"font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-asc