rif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Cambria;mso-hansi-font-family:Cambria\">一片百年紫標福元昌號普洱茶</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.0pt;\nfont-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"> 2</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:\n&quot;PMingLiU&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Cambria;mso-hansi-font-family:Cambria\">百</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.0pt;\nfont-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">44</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:\n&quot;PMingLiU&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Cambria;mso-hansi-font-family:Cambria\">萬港元溢價成交</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.0pt;\nfont-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"></span></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\nmso-line-height-alt:12.0pt\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></b></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\ntext-indent:25.55pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.13\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">香港<span lang=\"EN-US\">]</span>仕宏<span lang=\"EN-US\">2017</span>春季拍賣會<a name=\"OLE_LINK8\"></a><a name=\"OLE_LINK7\"></a><a name=\"OLE_LINK6\">已於上周假君悅酒店圓滿落槌，共舉行<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>項專場拍賣：「鑾器天香<span lang=\"EN-US\"> - </span>茶道·香道·花器專場」、「足吾所好<span lang=\"EN-US\"> - </span>古董級普洱茶及佳茗專場」、「御養尚品<span lang=\"EN-US\"> - </span>補品及佳釀專場」、「鐵硯春秋<span lang=\"EN-US\"> - </span>中國書畫專場<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span>」及「中國書畫（二）」，珍品迭出吸引全球藏家競投</a></span><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">。當中普洱茶專場</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">8</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">8</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">件</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">拍品之成交額<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>含</span><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">佣</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">金<span lang=\"EN-US\">) </span>超過<b><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>千<span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span>百萬港元</b>。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\ntext-indent:25.55pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.13\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:&quot;PMingLiU&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">對</span><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">此成績仕宏拍賣有限公司總裁周先生表示：「陳年普洱被稱為「可以喝的股票」，保存得宜的普洱茶是沒有保質期，越陳的茶只會越值錢，奇貨可居，成為收藏家競逐的心頭好。」<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\ntext-indent:25.55pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.13\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\ntext-indent:25.55pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.13\"><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">其中最引人入勝的為拍號<span lang=\"EN-US\">310</span>，一片約<span lang=\"EN-US\">341</span>克重 百年紫標福元昌號圓茶，經輪番競價後最終以</span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">2</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">百<span lang=\"EN-US\">44</span>萬港元</span></b><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">溢價成交，以一泡茶使用<span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span>克茶葉計算，</span><b><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif;\">就價值<span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span>萬元港幣</span></b><span style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:24.5pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:2.13\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: PMingLiU, serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shapetype id=\"_x0000_t75\" coordsize=\"21600,21600\"\no:spt=\"75\" o:preferrelative=\"t\" path=\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\" filled=\"f\"\nstroked=\"f\">\n<v:stroke joinstyle=\"miter\" ></v:stroke>\n<v:formulas>\n<v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"sum @0 1 0\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 @1\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @2 1 2\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"sum @0 0 1\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @6 1 2\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"sum @8 21600 0\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"sum @10 21600 0\" ></v:f>\n</v:formulas>\n<v:path o:extrusionok=\"f\" gradientshapeok=\"t\" o:connecttype=\"rect\" ></v:path>\n<o:lock v:ext=\"edit\" aspectratio=\"t\" ></o:lo