>)</span>謹訂於<span lang=\"EN-US\">2017</span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span>日假香港君悅酒店隆重舉行春季拍賣。分設四大類別專場：<b>中國書畫</b>﹑<b>古董名茶</b>﹑<b>茶具．香道．花器</b>及<b>養生尚品</b>專場，拍前總估價約</span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span></b><b><span style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"PMingLiU\",\"serif\";\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\'>千萬港元</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\">*</span><span style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:\n12.0pt;font-family:\"PMingLiU\",\"serif\"\'>。四大專場將於<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span>日亮相預展，<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span>日舉槌開拍，精巧奪目拍品琳瑯滿目，為藏家提供多</span><span style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"PMingLiU\",\"serif\";mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\'>元性質收藏選擇，期待各界朋友蒞臨共賞精采。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><p></p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"PMingLiU\",\"serif\";mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\'>　　</span><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"PMingLiU\",\"serif\";mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-language:ZH-HK\'>對於</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span><span style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:\n12.0pt;font-family:\"PMingLiU\",\"serif\";mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri\'>秋拍古董級普洱茶專場</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">31</span><span style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"PMingLiU\",\"serif\";mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\'>件拍品</span><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"PMingLiU\",\"serif\";mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-language:ZH-HK\'>以</span><b><span style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"PMingLiU\",\"serif\";mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri\'>逾三千萬港元</span></b><b><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"PMingLiU\",\"serif\";\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-language:\nZH-HK\'>成交，</span></b><span style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"PMingLiU\",\"serif\";\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\'>仕宏拍賣總裁周先生表示</span><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"PMingLiU\",\"serif\";\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-language:\nZH-HK\'>「</span><span style=\'font-family:\"PMingLiU\",\"serif\";mso-ascii-font-family:\nMingLiU;mso-hansi-font-family:MingLiU;mso-bidi-font-family:MingLiU;color:#333333\'>雅</span><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"PMingLiU\",\"serif\";\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-language:\nZH-HK\'>趣</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.xincha.com/s/chadao-1\"><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\"font-family: PMingLiU, serif; color: windowtext; text-decoration-line: none;\">茶道</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"PMingLiU\",\"serif\";\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-language:\nZH-HK\'>，源遠流長；</span><span style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"PMingLiU\",\"serif\";\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\'>為延續</span><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"PMingLiU\",\"serif\";\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-language:\nZH-HK\'>上屆之亮眼成續，今屆我們為</span><span style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\n\"PMingLiU\",\"serif\";mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\'>藏家覓得更多古</span><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"PMingLiU\",\"serif\";\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-language:\nZH-HK\'>董</span><span style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"PMingLiU\",\"serif\";\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\'>級普洱茶藏品。</span><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"PMingLiU\",\"serif\";\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-language:\nZH-HK\'>宋聘號﹑福元昌號﹑</span><span style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"PMingLiU\",\"serif\";\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\'>敬昌號</span><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"PMingLiU\",\"serif\";\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-language:\nZH-HK\'>﹑同興號‧向繩武等清代</span><span style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\n\"PMingLiU\",\"serif\";mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\'>傳奇</span><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"PMingLiU\",\"serif\";\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-language:\nZH-HK\'>茶莊，其藏品保留至今仍然完好，希望為拍</span><span style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"PMingLiU\",\"serif\";mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri\'>賣</span><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\n\"PMingLiU\",\"serif\";mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-fareast-language:ZH-HK\'>會再創新高。</span><span style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"PMingLiU\",\"serif\";mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri\'>」</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><p></p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"PMingLiU\",\"serif\";mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\'>　　</span><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"PMingLiU\",\"serif\";mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-language:ZH-HK\'>本屆另一亮點為</span><span style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"PMingLiU\",\"serif\";mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\'>新增設之御養尚品</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> - </span><span style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:\n12.0pt;font-family:\"PMingLiU\",\"serif\";mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri\'>補品及佳釀專場，加入市場上難求的花膠﹑鮑魚﹑人蔘﹑陳皮及珍稀洋酒；仕宏拍賣總裁周先生表示：「為保持市場競爭力，仕宏拍賣在拍品項目上大膽尋覓新角度</span><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"PMingLiU\",\"serif\";\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-language:\nZH-HK\'>。</span><span style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"PMingLiU\",\"serif\";\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\'>蘇軾</span><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"PMingLiU\",\"serif\";\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-language:\nZH-HK\'>於</span><span style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"PMingLiU\",\"serif\";\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\'>《浣溪沙》</span><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"PMingLiU\",\"serif\";\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-language:\nZH-HK\'>中提及</span><span style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"PMingLiU\",\"serif\";\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\'>『雪沫乳花浮午盞，蓼茸蒿筍試春盤。人間有味是清歡。』所表達</span><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"PMingLiU\",\"serif\";\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-language:\nZH-HK\'>他</span><span style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"PMingLiU\",\"serif\";\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\'>遍嘗人生百味後，最能讓生活適意的是初春曉寒中，品味茶飲與美食的清歡滋味，簡單且舒放至極的享受。我們希望</span><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\'mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"PMingLiU\",\"serif\";\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-fa