\">[</span>香港<span lang=\"EN-US\">]</span>仕宏<span lang=\"EN-US\">2015</span>秋季拍賣會預展將於<span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span>日及<span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span>日假</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\">香港君悅酒店</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:細明體;mso-bidi-font-family:細明體;color:#3E3E3E;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">向公眾開放，五項專場</span><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\">「鑾器天成</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\nmso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\"> - </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\">名茶御器專場」</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\">、<b>「朗吟奇香</b></span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\"> - </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\n&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\">沉香奇楠專場」</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\">、<b>「琳翠雅玩</b></span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\"> - </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\n&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\">玉器珍玩專場」</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\">、<b>「御釀芳奢</b></span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\"> - </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\n&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\">名酒珍釀專場</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\nmso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\n&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\">」及</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\nfont-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\">「<b>珍稀相機拍賣會」</b></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:細明體;mso-bidi-font-family:細明體;color:#3E3E3E;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">共展出<span lang=\"EN-US\">400</span>件珍貴臻品，期待各藏家蒞臨參觀。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:細明體;mso-bidi-font-family:\n細明體;color:#3E3E3E;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">　　陳年普洱被稱為「活態文物資產」，近十年来交易愈益驚人，奇貨可居，成為收藏家競逐的心頭好。仕宏秋拍中拍號<span lang=\"EN-US\">1032:</span><b>「百年極品 紅票宋聘</b>」是由有普洱茶教父之稱的清頤堂主人白水清先生所珍藏及提供，從清代乾倉儲存良好保存至今，達到頂峰階段的陳期，內飛清晰可見，重量更達<span lang=\"EN-US\">315</span>克，可謂是古董茶中最完整的餅茶之一。茶餅上不但有清頤堂主人白水清先生的親簽，他更為藏品親題「百年極品紅票宋聘　白水清」，為普洱藏家心中的夢幻逸品。本宋聘茶餅拍前估價高達<span lang=\"EN-US\">200</span>萬<span lang=\"EN-US\">-300</span>萬港元，有望躋身成交價最高之單片普洱。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; backg