font-family:\n細明體;mso-bidi-font-family:細明體;color:#3E3E3E;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">「百年極品 紅票宋聘」<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:細明體;mso-bidi-font-family:細明體;\ncolor:#3E3E3E;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp;</span></b></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:細明體;mso-bidi-font-family:\n細明體;color:#3E3E3E;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">　　<b>「福元昌號 福元昌圓茶」</b>曾於<span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span>年在北京拍賣以人民幣<span lang=\"EN-US\">1,035</span>萬元天價成交<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>一筒<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>，本次仕宏秋拍中亦見其踪，拍號<span lang=\"EN-US\">1033:</span>一片重<span lang=\"EN-US\">312</span>克之福元昌圓茶拍前估價達<span lang=\"EN-US\">100</span>萬<span lang=\"EN-US\">-200</span>萬港元，為紫票內飛，與「宋聘『紅標』」合稱「茶后」與「茶皇」。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\nid=\"圖片_x0020_1\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1026\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" alt=\"描述: /public/content/img_contents/LOTNO_1033_1.jpg\"\nstyle=\'width:230.25pt;height:126pt;visibility:visible\'>\n<v:imagedata src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\LH\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image004.jpg\"\no:title=\"LOTNO_103