>&nbsp;</span></p>\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"671\" style=\"width:503.25pt;margin-left:-5.7pt;border-collapse:collapse;border:none;\n    mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-yfti-tbllook:1184;mso-padding-alt:\n    0cm 1.4pt 0cm 1.4pt;mso-border-insideh:.5pt solid windowtext;mso-border-insidev:\n    .5pt solid windowtext\">\n    <tbody>\n        <tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:0;mso-yfti-firstrow:yes;height:56.25pt\">\n            <td width=\"671\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:503.25pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\n            mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 1.4pt 0cm 1.4pt;height:56.25pt\">\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">西際重譽大師<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\n            mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\n            Arial\">西際重譽為泉山御流十一代嫡承，是以名刹泉湧寺為中心傳承下來的香道流派。泉湧寺位於京都市內。作為天皇家族的菩提寺，泉湧寺也被稱為</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:微軟正黑體;mso-bidi-font-family:\n            Arial\">“</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\n            mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\n            Arial\">御寺</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:\n            微軟正黑體;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">”</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\n            font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:\n            Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">，是一座非常特殊的寺院。泉湧寺宗派始祖是入唐求法的弘法大師空海，開山始祖是入宋求法的月輪大師俊芿。寺內至今依然保存有皇族使用過的香道用具。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:微軟正黑體;mso-bidi-font-family:\n            Arial\"></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\n            mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\n            Arial\">泉山御流侍奉於泉湧寺（也稱泉山），奉京極（即佐佐木）導譽（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\n            10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:微軟正黑體;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">1306-1373</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:\n            Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">）為流派始祖。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:微軟正黑體;mso-bidi-font-family:\n            Arial\"></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:1;mso-yfti-lastrow:yes;height:56.25pt\">\n            <td width=\"671\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:503.25pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\n            border-top:none;mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;\n            padding:0cm 1.4pt 0cm 1.4pt;height:56.25pt\">\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">肖蓉</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\n            mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\n            Arial\">從</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:\n            微軟正黑體;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">2004</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\n            font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:\n            Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">年至今致力弘傳推廣中國傳統茶文化，師承香港茶人葉榮枝。現任湖南廣電茶頻道雅集總顧問及香港茶具博物館客席茶師。以茶修心，以茶悟道，以茶為媒復興中國失之久遠的傳統文化。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:微軟正黑體;mso-bidi-font-family:\n            Arial\"></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\nmso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\n新細明體\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">仕宏<span lang=\"EN-US\">2015</span>年秋季拍賣日程<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse;mso-yfti-tbllook:1184;mso-padding-alt:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\">\n    <tbody>\n        <tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:0;mso-yfti-firstrow:yes;height:17.85pt\">\n            <td width=\"656\" colspan=\"3\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 491.85pt; border: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; height: 17.85pt; background: rgb(199, 43, 27);\">\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:white\">預展　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　香港君悅酒店</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;color:white\">M</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:white\">層<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>畫堂<span lang=\"EN-US\"> (Drawing Room)</span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:1;height:17.15pt\">\n            <td width=\"168\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 125.9pt; border-style: none solid solid; border-right-color: windowtext; border-bottom-color: windowtext; border-left-color: windowtext; border-right-width: 1pt; border-bottom-width: 1pt;