=\"font-size:11.0pt;\nfont-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\">拍賣：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\n11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\">11</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\nfont-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\n11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\">28</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\nfont-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\">日</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\n11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\"></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:\n12.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\n新細明體\">　　仕宏拍賣秋拍將於</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:\n新細明體\">11</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\n新細明體\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:\n新細明體\">28</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\n新細明體\">日首次推出<b>「朗吟奇香</b></span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\nmso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\"> - </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\">沉香</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\">‧<b>奇楠專場」</b>拍賣，為傳承及推廣香道、茶道文化，預展期間將安排三場茗茶及六場香道環節，點上一炉香，奉上一壺茶，體驗不一樣的生活雅事，歡迎公眾參觀。由茶藝師肖蓉女士分別以本次拍品沖泡試茶；香道環節特意從日本邀請<b>「泉山御流十一代嫡承」西際重譽大師</b>親自前來教授與示範</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">香道體驗</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\">，不容錯過，費用全免，席次有限，敬請提前預約。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\"></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\n新細明體\">　　聞香不但能使人心靈重拾平靜，還有助消除壓力、提高專注力以及增強免疫力。希望藉著舉辦此次香道體驗活動，讓更多人能夠重新認識這歷史悠久的傳統教養，推廣香道文化以及提供一個讓繁忙的都市人在百忙之中歇息的空間。從松灰、燒炭、入炭、理灰、壓灰到打筋、開火窗、切香、入香、品香，層層環節，在煙氣氤氳中體會禪意凝思。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\"></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:\n新細明體\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\n新細明體\">【香道體驗內容】</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:\n新細明體\"></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:24.0pt;mso-para-margin-left:0gd;\ntext-indent:-24.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri\">1.<span style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;