ound-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse;border:none;mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;\n    mso-yfti-tbllook:1184;mso-padding-alt:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;mso-border-insideh:\n    .5pt solid windowtext;mso-border-insidev:.5pt solid windowtext\">\n    <tbody>\n        <tr>\n            <td width=\"666\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:499.85pt;border:none;background:gray;\n            padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\">\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;\n            font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:\n            Calibri;color:white\">「朗吟奇香</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;color:white\"> - </span></b><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;\n            font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:\n            Calibri;color:white\">沉香奇楠專場」精選拍品</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;color:white\"></span></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:1;height:21.3pt\">\n            <td width=\"666\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:499.85pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\n            border-bottom:none;mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-left-alt:\n            solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-right-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:\n            0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:21.3pt\">\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">LOT 2026.&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">沉水綠油奇楠　</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">(</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">長</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">27.5cm</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">，寬</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">12.7cm</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">，重</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">692 g)</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif; color: rgb(199, 43, 27);\">估價：</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; color: rgb(199, 43, 27);\">HK$4,500,000 – HK$6,800,000</span></b><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shapetype\n            id=\"_x0000_t75\" coordsize=\"21600,21600\" o:spt=\"75\" o:preferrelative=\"t\"\n            path=\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\" filled=\"f\" stroked=\"f\">\n            <v:stroke joinstyle=\"miter\" ></v:stroke>\n            <v:formulas>\n            <v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\" ></v:f>\n            <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 1 0\" ></v:f>\n            <v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 @1\" ></v:f>\n            <v:f eqn=\"prod @2 1 2\" ></v:f>\n            <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\" ></v:f>\n            <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\" ></v:f>\n            <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 0 1\" ></v:f>\n            <v:f eqn=\"prod @6 1 2\" ></v:f>\n            <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\" ></v:f>\n            <v:f eqn=\"sum @8 21600 0\" ></v:f>\n            <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\" ></v:f>\n            <v:f eqn=\"sum @10 21600 0\" ></v:f>\n            </v:formulas>\n            <v:path o:extrusionok=\"f\" gradientshapeok=\"t\" o:connecttype=\"rect\" ></v:path>\n            <o:lock v:ext=\"edit\" aspectratio=\"t\" ></o:lock>\n            </v:shapetype><v:shape id=\"_x0000_s1032\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style=\'position:absolute;\n            margin-left:277.05pt;margin-top:45.05pt;width:220pt;height:125.15pt;\n            z-index:-251651072;visibility:visible;mso-position-horizontal-relative:text;\n            mso-position-vertical-relative:text\' wrapcoords=\"-65 0 -65 21486 21600 21486 21600 0 -65 0\">\n            <v:imagedata src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\LH\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image001.png\"\n            o:title=\"\" ></v:imagedata>\n            <w:wrap type=\"tight\" ></w:wrap>\n        </v:shape><![endif]--><!--[if !vml]--><img width=\"293\" height=\"167\" src=\"/public/content/img_contents/LOTNO_2026_1.jpg\" align=\"left\" hspace=\"12\" v:shapes=\"_x0000_s1032\" alt=\"\"><!--[endif]--></p>\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">　　有道上品不雕，故此物保留了上天賜予的原始線條。綠油奇楠是奇楠中的頂級，是醇化了一定程度的熟奇楠，橫切面見綠多黃少，油脂均勻豐厚，入水即沉；尤其此香完整碩大，為加工開材成珠或收藏之頂級珍品。毋須點燃，聞之氣味芳香，點之更香氣沁溢，氣味清甜帶有絲絲涼意，直入肺腑，倍感心曠神怡，香品高雅。不施任何雕琢，造型保持天然完整的形態，加上香味極富韻味，是為最上乘之奇楠。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">　　沉香被譽為木中鑽石，而奇楠便是極品沉香中的極品，在整料沉香中通常只有非常小的一部分為奇楠，貴比黃金。如拍品般優質且巨大重達近七百克的綠油奇楠香材十分罕見，稀少難尋極其珍貴。奇楠集千百年天地靈氣，散發香氣同時亦以香喻人，大自然讓它受傷而它卻化苦為香；體現君子之品德，在人生受到挫折，只要能吸取教訓，面對後亦能轉化為流芳百世的靈性。將其置之書齋案頭，頓感身心開通。</span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#C72B1B\"></span></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:2;height:165.3pt\">\n            <td width=\"666\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:499.85pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\n            border-bottom:none;mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-left-alt:\n            solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-right-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:\n            0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:165.3pt\">\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt\">LOT 2028. </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:\n            Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">海南瓊脂國香　</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt\">(</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\n            &quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">尺寸不一，共重</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt\">37.4   g)</span></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:\n            Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;color:#C72B1B\">估價：</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\n            color:#C72B1B\">HK$180,000 – HK$300,000</span></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"/public/content/img_contents/LOTNO_2028_1.jpg\" width=\"200\" height=\"127\" alt=\"\"></p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td width=\"666\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:499.85pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\n            border-top:none;mso-border-left-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-bottom-alt:\n            solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-right-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:\n            0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\">\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">　　古籍記載：「海南沉香，一片萬錢，冠絕天下」。海南有瓊脂的美稱，自古以來已是出產最上乘沉香的產區。海南的沉香馨香遠聞，比一般沉香性質更溫潤，連詩人蘇東坡亦被迷倒，賦詞《沉香山子賦》讚頌之：「矧儋崖</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">(</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">今海南島</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">)</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">之異產，實超然而不群。既金堅而玉潤，亦鶴骨以龍筋。惟膏液之內足，故把握而兼斤</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">……</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">無一往之發烈，有無窮之氤氳。」</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">　　三塊國香氣味甘甜幽柔，散發淡淡仙楂味，奶香沁入心脾，擴散力極強，只需取少量已足夠滿室生香，歷久彌香。表面厚實感足，包漿完美，結油清晰可見，極黑有油。海南沉香於清後期幾乎枯絕，現今更為瀕臨絕種植物，世間難覓。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:4;height:37.6pt\">\n        </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table>					</div>', 'admin', 'admin', '1447257600', '1523325823', null, '1', null, null, '/public/pdf/content/1523008204.pdf', '/public/pdf/content/1523008202.pdf', null);
INSERT INTO `curio_content` VALUES ('24', 'L&H Autumn Auction 2015 To Be Hold on 28 Nov 2015, Estimated valued about HK$60 million', '仕宏2015年秋季拍賣將於11 月 28日舉槌 推出五大專場 呈獻珍稀瑰寶 總估值約 六千萬港元', '12', '', '<div class=\"pcontent\">\n<p>&nbsp;<img width=\"701\" height=\"3\" src=\"file:///C:/Users/LH/AppData/Local/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_image001.gif\" v:shapes=\"_x0000_s1026\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">Press Release</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;mso-bidi-font-family:\nArial;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN\"> [</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">For Immediate Release</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;mso-bidi-font-family:\nArial;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN\">]&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:\nSimSun;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;mso-bidi-font-family:\nArial;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">18<sup>th</sup> Nov., 2015</span></b><b><span lang=\"ZH-CN\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\nfont-family:SimSun;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN\">｜</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">HONG KONG</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:5.0pt\"></span></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-fareast-language:ZH-HK\">L&amp;H 2015 Autumn Auction is </span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-fareast-language:\nZH-CN\">Right Under the Hammer</span></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-fareast-language:ZH-HK\">Plenty of Rare Collections will be Presented in 5 Special Sessions:</span></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-fareast-language:ZH-HK\">Tea Ware Auction/ Agarwood Auction/ Jade Auction/ </span></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-fareast-language:ZH-HK\">Wine Auction/ the 6th Photographica Auction</span></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;mso-line-height-alt:\n12.0pt\"><b style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Preview: Nov 27<sup>th</sup>-28<sup>th</sup> | Auction: Nov 28<sup>th</sup></span></b><span style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif; font-size: 11pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 12pt;\">　</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:\n12.0pt\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 12pt;\"><span style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">L&amp;H Auction Co., Ltd (L&amp;H Auction) will present the autumn auction on Nov 28th</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">(Sat) at Grand Hyatt Hong Kong. The public preview will be on Nov 27th-28th. Besides the</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">\"L&amp;H Rare Photographica Auction\"</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">which has been highly&nbsp;expected</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">by the whole international photographica industry and the Tea Ware Auction which&nbsp;carries</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">on the</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">attention from&nbsp;collectors, there will also be Agarwood Auction, Jade Auction and Wine Auction this time. Over 400 precious lots in this autumn auction will be presented to public, the current estimated price is around</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">HKD60,000,000,&nbsp;which is a</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">great event&nbsp;that worths&nbsp;high expectation.</span><span style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">　　</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\nmso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">\"Carrying on the great result we have achieved in last auction, we arranged to present agarwood and Chinan with an individual session this time. The</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">great collection of rare Submerged Chinan and Hainan Agar makes it an unmissable opportunity to enjoy the incense. Meanwhile, inspired by the positive impacts from our previous experience of adding individual sessions, we divided the auction by categories with more lots, hoping that&nbsp;this arrangement can draw more attention of global collectors. The lots included 5 categories</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">--&nbsp;tea and tea ware, agarwood and Chinan, jade, fine wine,</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">and photographica</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">--</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">containing</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">plenty of rare treasures. Our purpose is to thank all collectors for their lasting support and trust, and we mean to make&nbsp;L&amp;H Auction&nbsp;a great</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">platform</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">for rare collection exchange&nbsp;around the world,\"</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">says Mr. Henry Chau, the CEO of L&amp;H Auction.</span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\nmso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">The preview of this autumn auction will officially go live&nbsp;from</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Nov 27th&nbsp;- 28th at Grand Hyatt Hong Kong in the Drawing Room of flat M. Public visit&nbsp;is</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">warmly welcomed. In addition, for promoting and sharing the</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">culture, 3 sessions</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">of tea ceremony and 6 sessions of incense ceremony</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">will be&nbsp;arranged. A professional&nbsp;tea&nbsp;art expert will host the tea ceremony sessions.&nbsp;For the&nbsp;incense ceremony sessions,&nbsp;it is particularly noteworthy&nbsp;that</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Master NISHIGIWA Shigetaka from Japan</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">has been invited&nbsp;to be the host. The registration is totally free</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">ofcharge with limited seats, so an appointment in advance in required.</span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p cl