style=\"font-size: 13pt;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">呈獻珍稀瑰寶</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13pt;\"></span></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: center;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">總估值約六千萬港元</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13pt;\"></span></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" align=\"center\" style=\"font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: center; line-height: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">名茶御器　沉香奇楠　玉器珍玩　名酒珍釀　珍稀相機</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" align=\"center\" style=\"font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: center; line-height: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">預</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">展：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">11</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">27-28</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">日</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;|&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">拍賣：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">11</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">28</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">日</span><span style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 12px; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">　</span><span style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">　</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" align=\"center\" style=\"font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: center; line-height: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"line-height: 12pt;\"><span style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">　　仕宏拍賣有限公司</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 11pt;\">（</span><span style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">仕宏拍賣</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 11pt;\">）</span><span style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">謹訂於</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 11pt;\">2015</span><span style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 11pt;\">11</span><span style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;28&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">日（星期六）假香港君悅酒店隆重舉行秋季拍賣會，公開預展日期為</span><span style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;<span lang=\"EN-US\">11&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;27-28</span><span style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">日。除國際相機界期待的盛會「<b>仕宏珍稀相機拍賣會」</b>外，去年引起廣大藏家關注的<b>「鑾器天成</b></span><b style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;<span lang=\"EN-US\">-&nbsp;</span></span></b><b style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">名茶御器專場」</span></b><span style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">，亦會再度推出，並推出精心規劃的<b>「朗吟奇香</b></span><b style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 12px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;-&nbsp;</span></b><b style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">沉香奇楠專場」</span></b><span style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">、<b>「琳翠雅玩</b></span><b style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 12px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">-&nbsp;</span></b><b style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">玉器珍玩專場」</span></b><span style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">、<b>「御釀芳奢</b></span><b style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 12px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;-&nbsp;</span></b><b style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">名酒珍釀專場</span></b><b style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 12px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">」</span></b><span style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">；</span><span style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">雲集</span><span style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">近</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 11pt;\">400</span><span style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">件珍寶，拍前總估價約</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 11pt;\">6,000&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">萬港元</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 11pt;\">*</span><span style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">，令人引頸以待。</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">　　仕宏拍賣總裁周先生表示：「承接上季沉香拍賣佳績，沉香及奇楠將於本次秋季拍賣中獨立以專場形式推出，稀世的沉水奇楠原材及世間難覓的海南瓊脂雲集，為不可錯過的聞香良機。同時受到上屆增加專場對市場有正面影響的啟發，本次拍賣會亦乘勝加入更多元拍賣，祈吸引全球藏家目光；拍品涵蓋茶葉及茶道具、沉香奇楠、玉石、名酒、相機五大類，當中更有不少稀世瑰寶，旨在答謝藏家們對我們的支持與信任，並希望仕宏拍賣成為蒐羅珍罕精品的絕佳平台。」</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">　　預展將於</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">11</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">27-28</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">日在香港君悅酒店</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">M</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">層</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">畫堂</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;(Drawing Room)</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">進行，歡迎公眾參觀。為傳承和推廣香道、茶道文化，預展期間將安排兩場茗茶及六場香道環節。由駐場茶藝師分別以本次拍品</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">(88</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">青普洱﹑孫義順三票老六安﹑九十年代</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">7542</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">及九六年真淳雅號</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">)</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">沖泡試茶；香道環節特意從日本邀請<b>「泉山御流十一代嫡承」西際重譽大師</b>親自前來教授與示範</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">香道體驗</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">，不容錯過，費用全免，席次有限，敬請提前預約。</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: justify;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">仕宏<span lang=\"EN-US\">2015</span>年秋季拍賣日程<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" ce