font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">香港仕宏</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">2015</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">春季拍賣會「鑾器天香」與「珍稀相機」專場已於上周五</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">5</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">29</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">日假君悅酒店在掌聲中完滿落槌，兩項專場總成交額約</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">3,200</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">萬港幣</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">(</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">含佣金，下同</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">)</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">。仕宏拍賣有限公司總裁周先生表示：「鑾器天香專場競投氣氛十分熱熾，表現令人滿意，其中沉香項目競投尤其激烈，體現藏家對珍罕的沉香熱切需求，我們將繼續寰環徵集搜羅更多元化的拍品，以傳承和推廣香道﹑茶道文化。」</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; text-indent: 24.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-c