 background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">相機連</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">Summilux-M 1.4/50mm&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">及快速過片器」競拍節奏同樣緊</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 細明體; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">湊，經</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">過現場及電話買家多輪競</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 細明體; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">投</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">，最終以約</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial