tial; background-repeat: initial;\"></span></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 13.3333339691162px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">為方便閣下瀏覽拍賣品，網頁版將陸續上載所有拍品：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 8pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><a href=\"http://www.lhauction.com.hk/\">www.lhauction.com.hk</a></span><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">　</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 細明體; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 13.3333339691162px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; border: none;\">\n    <tbody>\n        <tr>\n            <td width=\"656\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 491.85pt; border: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; background: gray;\">\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif; color: white;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif; color: white;\">「鑾器天香<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;-&nbsp;</span>沉香、名茶御器及金石古玩」專場精選拍品<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 13.3333339691162px;\"><img width=\"320\" height=\"241\" src=\"/public/content/img_contents/LOTNO_830_2.JPG\" align=\"left\" hspace=\"12\" v:shapes=\"圖片_x0020_1\" alt=\"\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Lot 830.&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">金壽堂造</span>&nbsp;</b><b><span style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">嵌金銀滿工</span>&nbsp;</b><b><span style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">京都皇家宮園景紋鐵壺</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 13.3333339691162px;\"><b><span style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);\">估價：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(192, 0, 0);\">HK$1,200,000 - HK$1,800,000</span></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 13.3333339691162px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">　　此藏品出自京都鐵壺代表堂號之一金壽堂，形制大氣雍容，尊貴絕美。罕見地採用滿工，鑲嵌金銀，鎏金等工藝，精巧非常地令壺身﹑提梁﹑摘鈕﹑壺肩﹑環付﹑壺流等細處皆金光熠熠，奢華瑰麗；三彎提梁鑲嵌十六瓣菊，通常為日本天皇家徽象徵，故本藏品應為皇家鍛造之御用珍品。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 13.3333339691162px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">　　壺側以萬壽菊伴竪排「大日本　金壽堂造」，器底「金壽堂造」方章，年份應為明治中晚期；提梁直立，包漿溫潤，古樸渾厚；壺身採用類岩石自然肌理設計，保留生鐵與鑄型間古雅紋路，延續了金壽堂一貫高雅素潔的特色，又對比強化了藏品表面鑲金嵌銀，滿工工藝之精湛奢華，大氣非常。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 13.3333339691162px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">　　本藏品難得壺蓋，壺身皆開光。壺蓋開光內細膩如繡地鎏金嵌銀出百卉爭妍之景，開光外巧妙運用或填實，或勾描的手法，令金銀菊滿佈盛放，花葉掩映交錯其中，一金一銀，一虛一實，璀璨中又見雅致，富麗中又見生機<span lang=\"EN-US\">;&nbsp;</span>搭配開光內景致，彷彿四季美景盡收眼底，應有盡有。壺身金窗開光處雕畫出了皇家園林一隅，近景櫻梅怒放，秀竹林立，又見松柏蒼勁，遮天連葉；遠景拱橋閣榭，林木蔥蘢其中，又見碧波隱約，水天一色，也巧用金銀虛實，將瑰麗景致的層次，生動，繁茂蔚然再現於咫尺窗內，爐火純青，嘆為觀止。壺身金窗外亦是滿雕金銀菊盛放，又窗底鑲刻波濤祥雲紋，整壺圖文組合寓意，盛世常在，永續尊貴。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 13.3333339691162px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 13.3333339691162px;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></b><b style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Lot 843.&nbsp;</span></b><b style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">至尊綠奇楠</span>&nbsp;</b><b style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">十二子超級沉水佛珠手串</span>&nbsp;</b><b style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);\">估價：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(192, 0, 0);\">HK$2,000,000 - HK$3,000,000</span></b></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 13.3333339691162px; text-align: justify;\"><img width=\"250\" height=\"185\" src=\"/public/content/img_contents/LOTNO_843_1.jpg\" align=\"left\" hspace=\"12\" v:shapes=\"圖片_x0020_1\" alt=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">　　綠奇楠被奉為奇楠中極品，整料難尋，而大型沉水香材更是價值連城；此藏品之佛珠直徑罕見達<span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span>毫米，且品相完好，皆來自同一塊香材；手串整重高達<span lang=\"EN-US\">58</span>克，一般同規格手串<span lang=\"EN-US\">51</span>克左右即可沉水，此手串重量遠超過一般沉水標準，入水秒沉，可謂稀世珍寶，天孕奇香。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 13.3333339691162px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">　　此串佛珠顆粒飽滿瑩潤，表面油脂凝重，墨綠而黏軟，稍作把玩則奇芳四溢，通體留香；生聞時已可感受麻涼入喉的穿透力，甘味如蜜，辛帶花香，韻雅而深遠；上爐後氣味層次豐富，頭香有花草芬芳，清爽細膩；中調甜意漸濃，有果韻裊裊，又時而馥鬱如花；漸入尾調時，杏乳香緩出，溫婉卻又明麗雅致，餘香恬然持久。</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 13.3333339691162px;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Lot 868.&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">「</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family: 細明體;\">可以興</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">」</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family: 細明體;\">茶磚　（<span lang=\"EN-US\">1927</span>年後，</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family: 細明體;\">內</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family: 細明體;\">飛印鹿鶴）</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);\">估價：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(192, 0, 0);\">HK$500,000 - HK$1,000,000</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\"></span></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 13.3333339691162px; text-align: justify;\"><img width=\"239\" height=\"165\" src=\"/public/content/img_contents/LOTNO_868_1.JPG\" align=\"left\" hspace=\"12\" v:shapes=\"圖片_x0020_1\" alt=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 細明體;\">　　可以興磚茶被稱為「磚中之王」，其茶之香氣優越甚少古董茶能與之比擬。<span lang=\"EN-US\">1927</span>年後的可以興茶磚存量甚少，據資料顯示，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 細明體;\">15</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 細明體;\">年前其留存量</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 細明體;\">僅</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 細明體;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 細明體;\">件</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 細明體;\">，</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 細明體;\">每件<span lang=\"EN-US\">160</span>片即<span lang=\"EN-US\">480</span>片而已</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 細明體;\">，</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 細明體;\">經<span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span>年的消耗</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 細明體;\">，</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 細明體;\">目前全球可能存留不到幾十片</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 細明體;\">，行情持續看漲 。可以興茶磚具備以下四個特點，也創造了普洱茶歷史上很多唯一：<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 13.3333339691162px; margin-left: 21.3pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -21.3pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 一．<span style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 細明體;\">可以興磚茶是普洱茶歷史上唯一的「十兩磚」，與當時及目前流行的<span lang=\"EN-US\">250</span>公克（六兩半）磚茶不同。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 13.3333339691162px; margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -36pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;二．<span style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 細明體;\">可以興磚茶是生茶磚的傑出代表，也是唯一存留下來的生茶磚。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 13.3333339691162px; margin-left: 21.3pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -21.3pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">三．<span style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 細明體;\">勐海茶聞名於世，以黑色為上佳。可以興磚茶就是以細黑條索、上好的勐海普洱茶菁制造的，堪稱黑色普洱茶的標本。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 13.3333339691162px; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 13.3333339691162px; margin-left: 21.3pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -21.3pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">四．<span style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 細明體;\">可以興磚茶改寫了普洱磚茶史，是最早的磚形茶。陳宗懋先生主編、上海文藝出版社的 《中國茶經》一書中，在《技術篇》部分「緊茶壓製」詞條中有言「緊茶過去是壓制成帶柄的心臟形，因包裝運輸不便，<span lang=\"EN-US\">1967</span>年後改成磚形，每塊磚重<span lang=\"EN-US\">0.25</span>公斤」。但從可以興的生</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 細明體;\">產</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 細明體;\">年份來看，應為最早的磚形茶。</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 細明體;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; border: none;\">\n    <tbody>\n        <tr>\n            <td width=\"656\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 491.85pt; border: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; background: gray;\">\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><b><span style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif; color: white;\">「珍稀相機」專場精選拍品<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: yellow;\"></span></span></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 13.3333339691162px;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Lot 1. Leitz</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">卡帶式原型袖珍相機　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Leitz Cassetta Prototype</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);\">估價：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(192, 0, 0);\">HK$1,200,000 – HK$1,800,000</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif; color: rgb(204, 0, 0);\"></span></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 13.3333339691162px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 20pt;\"><img width=\"249\" height=\"172\" src=\"/public/content/img_contents/LOTNO_1_1.JPG\" align=\"left\" hspace=\"12\" v:shapes=\"圖片_x0020_1\" alt=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">此台是罕見的原裝<span lang=\"EN-US\">16mm</span>的原型相機，機身刻有「<span lang=\"EN-US\">Cassetta</span>」字樣，從未正式投入生產，估計現存的<span lang=\"EN-US\">Cassetta</span>相機只有<span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span>至<span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span>台。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">徠卡於<span lang=\"EN-US\">1950</span>年代起開始研發袖珍相機，此<span lang=\"EN-US\">Cassetta</span>與同屬於袖珍相機的<span lang=\"EN-US\">Leica 16</span>相比，外觀及結構設計截然不同<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>可參閱<span lang=\"EN-US\">Lars Netopil \"PROTOTYPE LEICA\", p.411-417)</span>。此原型相機已接近完成階段，其鏡頭是由<span lang=\"EN-US\">ENNA Munich</span>設計，對焦功能甚至可以正常運作，按鈕為後期款，但快門及測光功能卻未能正常使用；雖然如此，此相機仍相當出色。機身的淺藍色皮革跟著名的<span lang=\"EN-US\">M3 Willi Stein (#7000XX)&nbsp;</span>十分相似。此拍品已經過<span lang=\"EN-US\">Paul-Henry van Hasbroeck</span>及<span lang=\"EN-US\">Lars Netopil</span>鑑定。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><p></p></span></span><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 13.3333339691162px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 20pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">&nbsp;</span><b style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Lot 60.&nbsp;</span></b><b style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">早期</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Leica</span></b><b style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">黑漆</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">MP</span></b><b style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">相機連</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Summilux-M 1.4/50mm&nbsp;</span></b><b style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">及快速過片器　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Leica MP Black Paint with Summilux-M 1.4/50mm and Leicavit &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></b><img width=\"300\" height=\"188\" src=\"/public/content/img_contents/LOTNO_60_1.JPG\" align=\"left\" hspace=\"12\" v:shapes=\"_x0000_s1027\" alt=\"\"><b style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);\">估價：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(192, 0, 0);\">HK$3,000,000 – HK$3,800,000</span></b></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 13.3333339691162px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">　　機身編號為<span lang=\"EN-US\">MP-122</span>的早期原裝黑漆<span lang=\"EN-US\">MP</span>相機及<span lang=\"EN-US\">Summilux-M 1.4/50mm</span>鏡頭<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;(#1703812)</span>，此套機曾於<span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span>年被刊登於德國徠卡權威雜誌《<span lang=\"EN-US\">VIDOM</span>》<span lang=\"EN-US\">101</span>期的<span lang=\"EN-US\">26 - 55</span>頁及封底中，作為介紹早期<span lang=\"EN-US\">MP</span>相機特別之處的鑒定藍本機；記錄的圖片及資料甚為豐富及詳盡，篇幅長達<span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span>頁。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 13.3333339691162px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">　　<span lang=\"EN-US\">MP</span>黑漆相機只有<span lang=\"EN-US\">138</span>台左右，機身號碼由<span lang=\"EN-US\">MP-013</span>至<span lang=\"EN-US\">MP-150 (</span>可參閱<span lang=\"EN-US\">James Lager Vol.I p.193)</span>。此機更是早期的油質黑漆相機，比後期的水質漆更為罕見珍貴。其機底號碼與機身相同，配有快速過片器、包裝盒、皮套等及《<span lang=\"EN-US\">VIDOM</span>》<span lang=\"EN-US\">101</span>期。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 13.3333339691162px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">　　此套機成色在<span lang=\"EN-US\">MP</span>黑漆相機中可說是上佳之選，而且可在<span lang=\"EN-US\">138</span>台<span lang=\"EN-US\">MP</span>中被挑選刊登於《<span lang=\"EN-US\">VIDOM</span>》中，無疑是十分難得，絕對是罕見的收藏品。</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 13.3333339691162px; text-align: justify;\"><b style=\"font-size: 13.3333339691162px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Lot 24.&nbsp;</span></b><b style=\"font-size: 13.3333339691162px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">著名小說家歐內斯特</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">·</span></b><b style=\"font-size: 13.3333339691162px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">米勒</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">·</span></b><b style=\"font-size: 13.3333339691162px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">海明威珍藏</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Leica IIIf</span></b><b style=\"font-size: 13.3333339691162px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">相機</span>&nbsp;<span lang=\"EN-US\">Leica IIIf with Summicron 2/5cm</span></b><b style=\"font-size: 13.3333339691162px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">“</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Hemingway</span></b><b style=\"font-size: 13.3333339691162px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">”</span></b><b style=\"font-size: 13.3333339691162px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif; color: rgb(204, 0, 0);\">　</span></b><b style=\"font-size: 13.3333339691162px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);\">估價：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(192, 0, 0);\">HK$200,000 – HK$300,000</span></b></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 13.3333339691162px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 13.3333339691162px; text-align: justify;\"><img width=\"260\" height=\"173\" src=\"/public/content/img_contents/LOTNO_24_10.JPG\" align=\"left\" hspace=\"12\" v:shapes=\"_x0000_s1028\" alt=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">　　這套<span lang=\"EN-US\">Leica IIIf</span>相機&nbsp;<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>機身編號<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;MP-122)</span>連<span lang=\"EN-US\">Summicron 2/5cm</span>鏡頭<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;(#1255243)</span>，原本由<span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span>世紀最著名的小說家之一的美國記者<span lang=\"EN-US\">/</span>作家–歐內斯特·海明威<span lang=\"EN-US\">(Ernest Hemingway)</span>所擁有；直至<span lang=\"EN-US\">1950</span>年代後期，他才將此套機轉贈予另一位著名的冒險小說作家愛迪生·馬歇爾<span lang=\"EN-US\">(Edison Marshall)</span>。有關資料可見此拍品隨附的信件。套機配有鏡頭前蓋及同樣於<span lang=\"EN-US\">1955</span>年生產的金屬相機套<span lang=\"EN-US\">MBROO</span>。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 13.3333339691162px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">　　歐內斯特·米勒·海明威（<span lang=\"EN-US\">Ernest Miller Hemingway</span>，<span lang=\"EN-US\">1899</span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">21</span>日－<span lang=\"EN-US\">1961</span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>日），&nbsp;<span lang=\"EN-US\">1939</span>年至<span lang=\"EN-US\">1960</span>年間，海明威在古巴定居，並寫下了聞名於世的代表作《老人與海》，並以此書獲得普立茲獎及諾貝爾文學獎。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 13.3333339691162px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 1