xt; border-left-color: windowtext; border-right-width: 1pt; border-bottom-width: 1pt; border-left-width: 1pt; padding: 0cm 1.4pt; height: 42.8pt;\">\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 6pt 0.0001pt 5.65pt; text-align: justify;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;\">有關</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Mr. Lars Netopil</span></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 5.65pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Mr. Lars Netopil</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;\">是國際間首屈一指的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Leica</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;\">相機真偽及估價鑑定專家，同時是德國徠卡歷史研究學會</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">(Leica Historica e.V.)</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;\">的副會長，兼現任徠卡公司</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">(Leica AG)</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;\">顧問。曾出版出版</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Leica</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;\">相機著作</span><i><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Prototype Leica</span></i><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;\">。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 13.3333339691162px; margin-left: 21.3pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -21.3pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 13.3333339691162px; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">*</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;\">估價不包括買家佣金</span></p>					</div>', '<div class=\"pcontent\">\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">仕宏2015年春季拍賣將於5月29日舉槌<br>\n</span></h3>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">總估值約四千萬港元<br>\n</span></h3>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</h3>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">近380件精選拍品於「鑾器天香」及「珍稀相機」專場同日舉行</span></h3>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\nmso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\n12.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\">仕宏拍賣謹訂於<b><span lang=\"EN-US\">2015</span>年 <span lang=\"EN-US\">5 </span>月 <span lang=\"EN-US\">29 </span>日</b>假<b>香港君悅酒店</b>盛大舉行春季拍賣會。屆時，近<span lang=\"EN-US\">380</span>件精選拍品將於「鑾器天香<span lang=\"EN-US\"> - </span>沉香、名茶御器及金石古玩」和「珍稀相機」專場上陸續登場，</span><span style=\"font-family:\n&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica\">廣大藏家將有機會一睹金壽堂傳世巨作</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Helvetica&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">-</span><span style=\"font-family:\n&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica\">皇家用滿工鑲金銀鐵壺、當代雕刻大師李鳳榮雕巨型沉水描金心經佛祖沉香牌及極品沉水奇楠手串、</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\">罕見於世的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Helvetica&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">1927</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:\nHelvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica\">年後「可以興」青普洱茶磚、估價超過百萬港幣的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Leitz</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">卡帶式原型袖珍相機</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Leitz Cassetta Prototype </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Helvetica&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">……</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\">等稀世珍品風采。</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\n新細明體\">本次拍賣預展將分別在<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">22</span>至<span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span>日於香港金鐘樂茶軒及<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span>至<span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span>日於銅鑼灣皇室堡進行，歡迎公眾參觀。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"line-height:12.0pt\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\n新細明體\">　　仕宏拍賣有限公司總裁周先生表示：「因應藏家及市場的需求，仕宏此屆再接再厲推出「鑾器天香</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Helvetica&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"> - </span><span style=\"font-family:\n&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica\">沉香、名茶御器及金石古玩專場</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\n12.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\">」，除豐富了拍品類別外，專場主題亦可見仕宏一貫堅持搜尋及呈現精品的宗旨和原則。此外，仕宏將在香港金鐘樂茶軒於預展期間舉辦「茶與茶道」分享會，誠邀香港著名茶與紫砂壺專家、香港茶道協會會長葉榮枝先生與藏家們分享其長達<span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span>年的普洱茶投資收藏經驗，機會難得，席位有限，需提前預約。周先生對此強調：「我們認為拍賣活動不僅是投資、收藏的平台，更是一個可以積極推動社會藝術鑑賞水平及文化涵養不斷提升平台，因此仕宏身體力行於其中，希望對行業及社會有所貢獻。」</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\n12.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\"><img src=\"/public/content/img_contents/LOTNO_1_1.JPG\" width=\"300\" height=\"178\" alt=\"\"><img src=\"/public/content/img_contents/LOTNO_840_2.JPG\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" alt=\"\"></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:8.0pt\">Lot 1. Leitz</span><span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;\nfont-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri\">卡帶式原型袖珍相機 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:8.0pt\"></span></p><p></p><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 8pt; text-align: center;\">國家禮品級&nbsp;(</span><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; text-align: center; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">共燒製三個，</span><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; text-align: center; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">同款曾</span><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; text-align: center; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">贈予中國前國家主席</span><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; text-align: center; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">胡錦濤</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 8pt; text-align: center;\">)</span><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\nmso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-TW;\nmso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">估價：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:8.0pt;\nfont-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family