    </tbody>\n</table>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shapetype\nid=\"_x0000_t75\" coordsize=\"21600,21600\" o:spt=\"75\" o:preferrelative=\"t\"\npath=\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\" filled=\"f\" stroked=\"f\">\n<v:stroke joinstyle=\"miter\" ></v:stroke>\n<v:formulas>\n<v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"sum @0 1 0\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 @1\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @2 1 2\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"sum @0 0 1\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @6 1 2\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"sum @8 21600 0\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"sum @10 21600 0\" ></v:f>\n</v:formulas>\n<v:path o:extrusionok=\"f\" gradientshapeok=\"t\" o:connecttype=\"rect\" ></v:path>\n<o:lock v:ext=\"edit\" aspectratio=\"t\" ></o:lock>\n</v:shapetype><v:shape id=\"圖片_x0020_1\" o:spid=\"_x0000_s1026\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\nstyle=\'position:absolute;margin-left:337.05pt;margin-top:9.75pt;width:143.95pt;\nheight:180.75pt;z-index:251661824;visibility:visible;\nmso-position-horizontal-relative:text;mso-position-vertical-relative:text\'>\n<v:imagedata src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\LH\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image001.png\"\no:title=\"\" ></v:imagedata>\n<w:wrap type=\"square\" ></w:wrap>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><!--[if !vml]--><img width=\"320\" height=\"241\" src=\"/public/content/img_contents/LOTNO_830_2.JPG\" align=\"left\" hspace=\"12\" v:shapes=\"圖片_x0020_1\" alt=\"\"><!--[endif]--><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Lot 830. </span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">金壽堂造</span> </b><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">嵌金銀滿工</span> </b><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">京都皇家宮園景紋鐵壺</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;color:#C00000\">估價：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#C00000\">HK$1,200,000 - HK$1,800,000</span></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\nmso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\">　　此藏品出自京都鐵壺代表堂號之一金壽堂，形制大氣雍容，尊貴絕美。罕見地採用滿工，鑲嵌金銀，鎏金等工藝，精巧非常地令壺身﹑提梁﹑摘鈕﹑壺肩﹑環付﹑壺流等細處皆金光熠熠，奢華瑰麗；三彎提梁鑲嵌十六瓣菊，通常為日本天皇家徽象徵，故本藏品應為皇家鍛造之御用珍品。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\nmso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\">　　壺側以萬壽菊伴竪排「大日本　金壽堂造」，器底「金壽堂造」方章，年份應為明治中晚期；提梁直立，包漿溫潤，古樸渾厚；壺身採用類岩石自然肌理設計，保留生鐵與鑄型間古雅紋路，延續了金壽堂一貫高雅素潔的特色，又對比強化了藏品表面鑲金嵌銀，滿工工藝之精湛奢華，大氣非常。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\nmso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\">　　本藏品難得壺蓋，壺身皆開光。壺蓋開光內細膩如繡地鎏金嵌銀出百卉爭妍之景，開光外巧妙運用或填實，或勾描的手法，令金銀菊滿佈盛放，花葉掩映交錯其中，一金一銀，一虛一實，璀璨中又見雅致，富麗中又見生機<span lang=\"EN-US\">; </span>搭配開光內景致，彷彿四季美景盡收眼底，應有盡有。壺身金窗開光處雕畫出了皇家園林一隅，近景櫻梅怒放，秀竹林立，又見松柏蒼勁，遮天連葉；遠景拱橋閣榭，林木蔥蘢其中，又見碧波隱約，水天一色，也巧用金銀虛實，將瑰麗景致的層次，生動，繁茂蔚然再現於咫尺窗內，爐火純青，嘆為觀止。壺身金窗外亦是滿雕金銀菊盛放，又窗底鑲刻波濤祥雲紋，整壺圖文組合寓意，盛世常在，永續尊貴。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></b><b style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Lot 843. </span></b><b style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family:\n&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">至尊綠奇楠</span> </b><b style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">十二子超級沉水佛珠手串</span> </b><b style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;color:#C00000\">估價：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#C00000\">HK$2,000,000 - HK$3,000,000</span></b></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shapetype\nid=\"_x0000_t75\" coordsize=\"21600,21600\" o:spt=\"75\" o:preferrelative=\"t\"\npath=\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\" filled=\"f\" stroked=\"f\">\n<v:stroke joinstyle=\"miter\" ></v:stroke>\n<v:formulas>\n<v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"sum @0 1 0\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 @1\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @2 1 2\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"sum @0 0 1\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @6 1 2\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"sum @8 21600 0\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"sum @10 21600 0\" ></v:f>\n</v:formulas>\n<v:path o:extrusionok=\"f\" gradientshapeok=\"t\" o:connecttype=\"rect\" ></v:path>\n<o:lock v:ext=\"edit\" aspectratio=\"t\" ></o:lock>\n</v:shapetype><v:shape id=\"圖片_x0020_1\" o:spid=\"_x0000_s1026\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\nstyle=\'position:absolute;left:0;text-align:left;margin-left:328.05pt;\nmargin-top:377.95pt;width:162pt;height:138.75pt;z-index:251658752;\nvisibility:visible;mso-position-horizontal-relative:margin;\nmso-position-vertical-relative:margin\'>\n<v:imagedata src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\LH\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image001.png\"\no:title=\"\" croptop=\"2462f\" cropbottom=\"2067f\" cropleft=\"5659f\" cropright=\"5306f\" ></v:imagedata>\n<w:wrap type=\"square\" anchorx=\"margin\" anchory=\"margin\" ></w:wrap>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><!--[if !vml]--><img width=\"250\" height=\"185\" src=\"/public/content/img_contents/LOTNO_843_1.jpg\" align=\"left\" hspace=\"12\" v:shapes=\"圖片_x0020_1\" alt=\"\"><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:\n10.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\">　　綠奇楠被奉為奇楠中極品，整料難尋，而大型沉水香材更是價值連城；此藏品之佛珠直徑罕見達<span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span>毫米，且品相完好，皆來自同一塊香材；手串整重高達<span lang=\"EN-US\">58</span>克，一般同規格手串<span lang=\"EN-US\">51</span>克左右即可沉水，此手串重量遠超過一般沉水標準，入水秒沉，可謂稀世珍寶，天孕奇香。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\">　　此串佛珠顆粒飽滿瑩潤，表面油脂凝重，墨綠而黏軟，稍作把玩則奇芳四溢，通體留香；生聞時已可感受麻涼入喉的穿透力，甘味如蜜，辛帶花香，韻雅而深遠；上爐後氣味層次豐富，頭香有花草芬芳，清爽細膩；中調甜意漸濃，有果韻裊裊，又時而馥鬱如花；漸入尾調時，杏乳香緩出，溫婉卻又明麗雅致，餘香恬然持久。</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Lot 868. </span></b><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\n12.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\">「</span></b><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:細明體\">可以興</span></b><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\n新細明體\">」</span></b><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:細明體\">茶磚　（<span lang=\"EN-US\">1927</span>年後，</span></b><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:細明體;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\">內</span></b><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:細明體\">飛印鹿鶴）</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;color:#C00000\">估價：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#C00000\">HK$500,000 - HK$1,000,000</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\n12.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\"></span></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shapetype\nid=\"_x0000_t75\" coordsize=\"21600,21600\" o:spt=\"75\" o:preferrelative=\"t\"\npath=\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\" filled=\"f\" stroked=\"f\">\n<v:stroke joinstyle=\"miter\" ></v:stroke>\n<v:formulas>\n<v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"sum @0 1 0\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 @1\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @2 1 2\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"sum @0 0 1\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @6 1 2\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"sum @8 21600 0\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"sum @10 21600 0\" ></v:f>\n</v:formulas>\n<v:path o:extrusionok=\"f\" gradientshapeok=\"t\" o:connecttype=\"rect\" ></v:path>\n<o:lock v:ext=\"edit\" aspectratio=\"t\" ></o:lock>\n</v:shapetype><v:shape id=\"圖片_x0020_1\" o:spid=\"_x0000_s1026\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\nstyle=\'position:absolute;left:0;text-align:left;margin-left:306.3pt;\nmargin-top:6pt;width:179.25pt;height:123.75pt;z-index:251659776;visibility:visible\'>\n<v:imagedata src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\LH\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image001.png\"\no:title=\"\" ></v:imagedata>\n<w:wrap type=\"square\" ></w:wrap>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><!--[if !vml]--><img width=\"239\" height=\"165\" src=\"/public/content/img_contents/LOTNO_868_1.JPG\" align=\"left\" hspace=\"12\" v:shapes=\"圖片_x0020_1\" alt=\"\"><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:\n10.0pt;font-family:細明體\">　　可以興磚茶被稱為「磚中之王」，其茶之香氣優越甚少古董茶能與之比擬。<span lang=\"EN-US\">1927</span>年後的可以興茶磚存量甚少，據資料顯示，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:細明體;mso-bidi-font-family:Times\">15</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:細明體;mso-bidi-font-family:Times\">年前其留存量</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:細明體;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\">僅</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:細明體;mso-bidi-font-family:Times\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:細明體;mso-bidi-font-family:Times\">件</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:細明體\">，</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\nfont-family:細明體;mso-bidi-font-family:Times\">每件<span lang=\"EN-US\">160</span>片即<span lang=\"EN-US\">480</span>片而已</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:細明體\">，</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:細明體;mso-bidi-font-family:Times\">經<span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span>年的消耗</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:細明體\">，</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:細明體;mso-bidi-font-family:Times\">目前全球可能存留不到幾十片</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:細明體\">，行情持續看漲 。可以興茶磚具備以下四個特點，也創造了普洱茶歷史上很多唯一：<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.3pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-21.3pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 一．<span style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:細明體\">可以興磚茶是普洱茶歷史上唯一的「十兩磚」，與當時及目前流行的<span lang=\"EN-US\">250</span>公克（六兩半）磚茶不同。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-36.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;二．<span style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:細明體\">可以興磚茶是生茶磚的傑出代表，也是唯一存留下來的生茶磚。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.3pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-21.3pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\">三．<span style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:細明體\">勐海茶聞名於世，以黑色為上佳。可以興磚茶就是以細黑條索、上好的勐海普洱茶菁制造的，堪稱黑色普洱茶的標本。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.3pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-21.3pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\">四．<span style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:細明體\">可以興磚茶改寫了普洱磚茶史，是最早的磚形茶。陳宗懋先生主編、上海文藝出版社的 《中國茶經》一書中，在《技術篇》部分「緊茶壓製」詞條中有言「緊茶過去是壓制成帶柄的心臟形，因包裝運輸不便，<span lang=\"EN-US\">1967</span>年後改成磚形，每塊磚重<span lang=\"EN-US\">0.25</span>公斤」。但從可以興的生</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\nfont-family:細明體;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\">產</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\nfont-family:細明體\">年份來看，應為最早的磚形茶。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\nfont-family:細明體\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse;border:none;mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;\n    mso-yfti-tbllook:1184;mso-padding-alt:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;mso-border-insideh:\n    .5pt solid windowtext;mso-border-insidev:.5pt solid windowtext\">\n    <tbody>\n        <tr>\n            <td width=\"656\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:491.85pt;border:none;background:gray;\n            padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\">\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;\n            font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:white\">「珍稀相機」專場精選拍品<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background:yellow;mso-highlight:yellow\"></span></span></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Lot 1. Leitz</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri\">卡帶式原型袖珍相機　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Leitz Cassetta Prototype</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;color:#C00000\">估價：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#C00000\">HK$1,200,000 – HK$1,800,000</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\nfont-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;color:#CC0000\"></span></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\ntext-indent:20.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shapetype\nid=\"_x0000_t75\" coordsize=\"21600,21600\" o:spt=\"75\" o:preferrelative=\"t\"\npath=\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\" filled=\"f\" stroked=\"f\">\n<v:stroke joinstyle=\"miter\" ></v:stroke>\n<v:formulas>\n<v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"sum @0 1 0\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 @1\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @2 1 2\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"sum @0 0 1\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @6 1 2\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"sum @8 21600 0\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\" ></v:f>\n<v:f eqn=\"sum @10 21600 0\" ></v:f>\n</v:formulas>\n<v:path o:extrusionok=\"f\" gradientshapeok=\"t\" o:connecttype=\"rect\" ></v:path>\n<o:lock v:ext=\"edit\" aspectratio=\"t\" ></o:lock>\n</v:shapetype><v:shape id=\"圖片_x0020_1\" o:spid=\"_x0000_s1026\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\nstyle=\'position:absolute;left:0;text-align:left;margin-left:301.8pt;\nmargin-top:193.3pt;width:186.75pt;height:129pt;z-index:251654656;visibility:visible;\nmso-position-horizontal-relative:margin;mso-position-vertical-relative:margin\'>\n<v:imagedata src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\LH\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image001.png\"\no:title=\"\" croptop=\"1824f\" cropbottom=\"3368f\" cropleft=\"3636f\" cropright=\"2846f\" ></v:imagedata>\n<w:wrap type=\"square\" anchorx=\"margin\" anchory=\"margin\" ></w:wrap>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><!--[if !vml]--><img width=\"249\" height=\"172\" src=\"/public/content/img_contents/LOTNO_1_1.JPG\" align=\"left\" hspace=\"12\" v:shapes=\"圖片_x0020_1\" alt=\"\"><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:\n10.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\">此台是罕見的原裝<span lang=\"EN-US\">16mm</span>的原型相機，機身刻有「<span lang=\"EN-US\">Cassetta</span>」字樣，從未正式投入生產，估計現存的<span lang=\"EN-US\">Cassetta</span>相機只有<span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span>至<span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span>台。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\nfont-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\">徠卡於<span lang=\"EN-US\">1950</span>年代起開始研發袖珍相機，此<span lang=\"EN-US\">Cassetta</span>與同屬於袖珍相機的<span lang=\"EN-US\">Leica 16</span>相比，外觀及結構設計截然不同<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>可參閱<span lang=\"EN-US\">Lars Netopil \"PROTOTYPE LEICA\", p.411-417)</span>。此原型相機已接近完成階段，其鏡頭是由<span lang=\"EN-US\">ENNA Munich</span>設計，對焦功能甚至可以正常運作，按鈕為後期款，但快門及測光功能卻未能正常使用；雖然如此，此相機仍相當出色。機身的淺藍色皮革跟著名的<span lang=\"EN-US\">M3 Willi Stein (#7000XX) </span>十分相似。此拍品已經過<span lang=\"EN-US\">Paul-Henry van Hasbroeck</span>及<span lang=\"EN-US\">Lars Netopil</span>鑑定。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><p></p></span></span><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\ntext-indent:20.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\">&nbsp;</span><b style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Lot 60.&nbsp;</span></b><b style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">早期</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Leica</span></b><b style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">黑漆</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">MP</span></b><b style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">相機連</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Summilux-M 1.4/50mm&nbsp;</span></b><b style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">及快速過片器　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Leica MP Black Paint with Summilux-M 1.4/50mm and Leicavit &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></b><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape id=\"_x0000_s1027\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\nstyle=\'position:absolute;margin-left:255.55pt;margin-top:343.1pt;width:248.75pt;\nheight:141.3pt;z-index:251655680;visibility:visible;\nmso-position-horizontal-relative:margin;mso-position-vertical-relative:margin\'>\n<v:imagedata src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\LH\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image003.png\"\no:title=\"\" croptop=\"2828f\" ></v:imagedata>\n<w:wrap type=\"square\" anchorx=\"margin\" anchory=\"margin\" ></w:wrap>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><!--[if !vml]--><img width=\"300\" height=\"188\" src=\"/public/content/img_contents/LOTNO_60_1.JPG\" align=\"left\" hspace=\"12\" v:shapes=\"_x0000_s1027\" alt=\"\"><b style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:#C00000\">估價：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#C00000\">HK$3,000,000 – HK$3,800,000</span></b></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\">　　機身編號為<span lang=\"EN-US\">MP-122</span>的早期原裝黑漆<span lang=\"EN-US\">MP</span>相機及<span lang=\"EN-US\">Summilux-M 1.4/50mm</span>鏡頭<span lang=\"EN-US\"> (#1703812)</span>，此套機曾於<span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span>年被刊登於德國徠卡權威雜誌《<span lang=\"EN-US\">VIDOM</span>》<span lang=\"EN-US\">101</span>期的<span lang=\"EN-US\">26 - 55</span>頁及封底中，作為介紹早期<span lang=\"EN-US\">MP</span>相機特別之處的鑒定藍本機；記錄的圖片及資料甚為豐富及詳盡，篇幅長達<span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span>頁。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\">　　<span lang=\"EN-US\">MP</span>黑漆相機只有<span lang=\"EN-US\">138</span>台左右，機身號碼由<span lang=\"EN-US\">MP-013</span>至<span lang=\"EN-US\">MP-150 (</span>可參閱<span lang=\"EN-US\">James Lager Vol.I p.193)</span>。此機更是早期的油質黑漆相機，比後期的水質漆更為罕見珍貴。其機底號碼與機身相同，配有快速過片器、包裝盒、皮套等及《<span lang=\"EN-US\">VIDOM</span>》<span lang=\"EN-US\">101</span>期。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體\">　　此套機成色在<span lang=\"EN-US\">MP</span>黑漆相機中可說是上佳之選，而且可在<span lang=\"EN-US\">138</span>台<span lang=\"EN-US\">MP</span>中被挑選刊登於《<span lang=\"EN-US\">VIDOM</span>》中，無疑是十分難得，絕對是罕見的收藏品。</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><b style=\"font-size: 13.3333339691162px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Lot 24.&nbsp;</span></b><b style=\"font-size: 13.3333339691162px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">著名小說家歐內斯特</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">·</span></b><b style=\"font-size: 13.333333969116