-bottom:0cm;mso-para-margin-left:\n            .47gd;mso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:\n            微軟正黑體;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:windowtext;\n            mso-font-kerning:1.0pt\">　　以香港為基地的仕宏拍賣有限公司成立於</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\n            微軟正黑體;color:windowtext;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt\">2013</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:\n            微軟正黑體;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:windowtext;\n            mso-font-kerning:1.0pt\">年，秉承「仕以高品而宏」之專業態度及宗旨，力求為收藏興趣愈益多元化的藏家們提供炙手可熱的藏品，將旗下拍賣活動打造成為收藏家們搜尋頂級珍品的良機盛會。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\n            mso-fareast-font-family:微軟正黑體;color:windowtext;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt\"></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n            <p class=\"Default\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:12.7pt;margin-bottom:\n            0cm;margin-left:5.65pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-para-margin-top:0cm;\n            mso-para-margin-right:1.06gd;mso-para-margin-bottom:0cm;mso-para-margin-left:\n            .47gd;mso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:\n            微軟正黑體;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:windowtext;\n            mso-font-kerning:1.0pt\">仕宏拍賣在提供專業拍賣服務的同時，也積極投身於相關文化的發展及傳播中：公司於過往兩年在北京及香港分別舉辦了徠卡收藏交流會，並難得地邀請到了著名徠卡歷史學家﹑身兼美國徠卡歷史學會會長詹姆斯</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\n            mso-fareast-font-family:微軟正黑體;color:windowtext;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt\">•</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:\n            微軟正黑體;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:windowtext;\n            mso-font-kerning:1.0pt\">拉格</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\n            font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:微軟正黑體;color:windowtext;\n            mso-font-kerning:1.0pt\">(James L. Lager)</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\n            mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:微軟正黑體;mso-hansi-font-family:\n            Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:windowtext;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt\">及德國徠卡歷史研究學會副會長</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\n            mso-fareast-font-family:微軟正黑體;color:windowtext;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt\">Mr.Lars   Netopil</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;\n            mso-fareast-font-family:微軟正黑體;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:\n            Arial;color:windowtext;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt\">與會演講，提供徠卡愛好者及收藏家們與徠卡大師面對面交流的寶貴機會，反應熱烈，深受好評。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\n            mso-fareast-font-family:微軟正黑體;color:windowtext;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt\"></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n            <p class=\"Default\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:12.7pt;margin-bottom:\n            0cm;margin-left:5.65pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-para-margin-top:0cm;\n            mso-para-margin-right:1.06gd;mso-para-margin-bottom:0cm;mso-para-margin-left:\n            .47gd;mso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:\n            微軟正黑					</div>\n</div>\n\n				</td>\n			</tr>\n			</table>\n\n\n\n		</div>\n	</td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n	<td valign=\" top=\"\">\n		</span></p><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" align=\"center\" width=\"979