;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\n細明體\">2014</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:細明體;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:\nArial;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">年秋季拍賣精彩可期</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\nmso-fareast-font-family:細明體\"></span></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;mso-line-height-alt:\n0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;\nfont-family:細明體;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">呈獻珍稀相機</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\nmso-fareast-font-family:細明體\"> </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:細明體;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:\nArial;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">及</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\nmso-fareast-font-family:細明體\"> </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:細明體;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:\nArial;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">鐵醉茶香</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\nmso-fareast-font-family:細明體\">—</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:細明體;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:\nArial;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">沉香．茶道具專場拍賣</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\nmso-fareast-font-family:細明體\"></span></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;mso-line-height-alt:\n0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;\nfont-family:細明體;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">超過三百件精美拍品</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\nmso-fareast-font-family:細明體\"> </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:細明體;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:\nArial;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">總估值逾三千二百萬</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\nmso-fareast-font-family:細明體\"></span></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 細明體;\">以香港為基地的仕宏拍賣秋拍將於</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">2014</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 細明體;\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">11</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 細明體;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">8</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 細明體;\">日舉槌，除一年兩屆的珍稀相機拍賣外，更特別呈獻名為「鐵醉茶香</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">—</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 細明體;\">沉香．茶道具專場」，近</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">360</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 細明體;\">件珍稀古董相機﹑鏡頭﹑沉香﹑鐵壺及茶道具拍品，總估值逾三千二百萬的精品將分上下半場悉數推出。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 細明體;\">　　仕宏拍賣有限公司總裁周先生表示：「作為新晉的拍賣行，我們致力為廣大相機藏家提供最頂級的拍品和服務，在過往三屆拍賣中得到眾多收藏家信賴與肯定，鑒於亞洲地區對茶道及香道的文化逐漸興盛，為滿足更多藏家的需求，我們決定推出新的拍賣專場，以沉香及茶道具為主線的鐵醉茶香以饕藏家。」</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 細明體;\">　　部份精選拍品已於九月份率先分別在北京的徠卡百年收藏展及中國國際沉香文化博覽會中展出，引起國內藏家熱烈討論與垂詢。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 細明體;\">　　香港的珍稀相機拍品預展將於</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">11</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 細明體;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">6</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 細明體;\">日至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">8</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 細明體;\">日進行推出共</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">221</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 細明體;\">件相機﹑鏡頭及配件。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right:6.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 細明體;\">　　鐵醉茶香秋拍拍品則於</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">10</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 細明體;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">31</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 細明體;\">日至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">11</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 細明體;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 細明體;\">日進行預展，共</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">136</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 細明體;\">件珍貴鐵壺﹑沉香茶道將悉數展出，同時每天特設四場免費茗茶</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">/</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 細明體;\">品香時段。茗茶環節由駐場茶藝師分別<u>以本次拍品沖泡試茶</u></span><b><u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">(</span></u></b><b><u><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 細明體;\">包括</span></u></b><b><u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">90</span></u></b><b><u><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 細明體;\">年代</span></u></b><b><u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">8582</span></u></b><b><u><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 細明體;\">青餅﹑</span></u></b><b><u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-fam