erif&quot;\">，共呈獻<span lang=\"EN-US\">288</span>件拍品供全球買家競拍，總成交額超過<span lang=\"EN-US\">3,900</span>萬港元<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>含佣金<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>。仕宏拍賣有限公司總裁周先生表示：「本次只是第三屆拍賣，但總成交價已躍升為同類專門相機拍賣會的第二位，足證明相機拍賣在大中華區的吸引力，及本屆拍品的質素，整體成交價比第二屆增長達兩成。」<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:21.3pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:2.13\"><img src=\"/public/content/img_contents/acution_web.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 18.66666603088379px; text-indent: 0px;\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:17.05pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:2.13\"><b><span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">仕宏拍賣第三屆拍賣會現場<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\ntext-indent:21.3pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.13\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\nfont-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">為慶祝<span lang=\"EN-US\">Leica</span>一百周年，仕宏拍賣推出的多部<span lang=\"EN-US\">Leica</span>百年經典作品皆成為買家關注的目標，現場熱烈的氣氛被<span lang=\"EN-US\">Leica</span>的代表作品拍賣編號<span lang=\"EN-US\">80</span>的<span lang=\"EN-US\">Leica MP</span>黑漆推至高潮，最終以<span lang=\"EN-US\">495</span>萬港元<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>含佣金<span lang=\"EN-US\">) </span>落槌成為本場最高價拍品，該機是僅生產<span lang=\"EN-US\">138</span>台<span lang=\"EN-US\">MP</span>黑漆版的其中一台，機身號碼為<span lang=\"EN-US\">141</span>，並且由名攝影師<span lang=\"EN-US\">Eric Schaal</span>所擁有，當年只有此般出色的專業攝影師及極少數的記者才能擁有徠卡<span lang=\"EN-US\">MP</span>相機。拍品配有供<span lang=\"EN-US\">MP</span>使用的同期黑漆銅卡口鏡頭<span lang=\"EN-US\">Summicron-M 2/50mm(#1468980)</span>及連同的<span lang=\"EN-US\">Eric Schaal</span>人像攝影集《<span lang=\"EN-US\">ERIC SCHAAL PHOTOGRAPH</span>》，書中更有其親人親筆證明<span lang=\"EN-US\">Eric Schaal</span>直至去世前一年依然用此台<span lang=\"EN-US\">MP</span>為他的至親拍攝，足見此機在<span lang=\"EN-US\">Eric Schaal</span>心目中是何等重要。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\ntext-indent:21.3pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.13\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\nfont-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">拍賣會後舉行由德國徠卡歷史研究學會副長<span lang=\"EN-US\">Mr. Lars Netopil</span>主講的分享會，現場吸引眾多<span lang=\"EN-US\">Leica</span>愛好者參與，分享交流古董相機欣賞及收藏心得，推動香港珍稀相機的收藏文化。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:21.3pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:2.13\"><img src=\"/public/content/img_contents/wade4373_web.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 18.66666603088379px; text-indent: 37.733333587646484px;\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:17.05pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:2.13\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:8.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">Mr. Lars Netopil </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">徠卡分享會現場<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\nArial\">最高成交價拍品介紹<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"678\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse;mso-table-layout-alt:fixed;border:none;\n    mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-yfti-tbllook:1184;mso-padding-alt:\n    0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;mso-border-insideh:.5pt solid windowtext;mso-border-insidev:\n    .5pt solid windowtext\">\n    <tbody>\n        <tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:0;mso-yfti-firstrow:yes;height:24.05pt\">\n            <td width=\"64\" style=\"width:47.95pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n            solid windowtext .5pt;background:gray;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5