width=\"633\" style=\"margin-left:8.5pt;border-collapse:collapse;mso-table-layout-alt:fixed;\n    border:none;mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-padding-alt:0cm 1.4pt 0cm 1.4pt;\n    mso-border-insideh:.5pt solid windowtext;mso-border-insidev:.5pt solid windowtext\">\n    <tbody>\n        <tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:0;mso-yfti-firstrow:yes;height:20.5pt\">\n            <td width=\"633\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:474.85pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\n            mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;background:gray;padding:0cm 1.4pt 0cm 1.4pt;\n            height:20.5pt\">\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\n            &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">本季精選拍品</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\n            9.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#464646;\n            background:white\"></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:1;height:20.5pt\">\n            <td width=\"633\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:474.85pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\n            border-top:none;mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;\n            padding:0cm 1.4pt 0cm 1.4pt;height:20.5pt\">\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\n            mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">Lot 80. </span></u></b><b><u><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;\n            font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-font-kerning:\n            0pt\">著名攝影師<span lang=\"EN-US\"> Eric Schaal Leica MP </span>黑漆相機<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></u></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\n            mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">Serial no. MP-141, 1957, B+</span></u></b></p>\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\n            mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"></span></u></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\n            tab-stops:119.25pt\"><span lang=\"X-NONE\" style=\"font-size: 0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; border: 1pt none black; padding: 0cm; background-color: black; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\n            tab-stops:119.25pt\"><img src=\"/public/content/img_contents/LOTNO_80_1.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"285\" style=\"text-align: center;\" alt=\"\"></p>\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\n            tab-stops:119.25pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">本拍品是僅生產</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">138</span><span style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">台</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">MP</span><span style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">黑漆版的其中一台，機身號碼為</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">141</span><span style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">，並且由二十世紀知名攝<br>\n            影師</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">Eric Schaal</span><span style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">所擁有。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">Eric Schaal</span><span style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">擅長人物攝影，曾替無數藝術家和學者拍攝肖像，<br>\n            當中包括物理學家</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">Albert Einstrin (</span><span style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">愛因斯坦</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">)</span><span style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">及超現實主義大師</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">Salvador Dali (</span><span style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">達利</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">)</span><span style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">等。<br>\n            當年只有此般出色的專業攝影師及極少數的記者才能擁有徠卡</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">MP</span><span style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">相機，相機所配有的<br>\n            </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">LEICAVIT(</span><span style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">快速過片器</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">)</span><span style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">最多可以每秒過片兩張，這功能可滿足專業攝影師的不同要求。<br>\n            而</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">Eric Schaal</span><span style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">擁有的還是更罕見的黑漆版本。此乃早期的原裝</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">MP</span><span style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">黑漆相機</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">機底同樣刻<br>\n            有與機身相同的“</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">P 141</span><span style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">”，相機保留原廠原裝狀態。配有供</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">MP</span><span style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">使用的同期黑漆銅卡口<br>\n            鏡頭</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">Summicron-M 2/50mm(#1468980)</span><span style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">連前蓋。拍品連同的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">Eric   Schaal</span><span style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">人像攝影集<br>\n            《</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">ERIC SCHAAL PHOTOGRAPH</span><span style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">》，在書中，其親人親筆證明</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">Eric Schaal</span><span style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">直至去世前<br>\n            一年依然用此台</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">MP</span><span style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">為他的至親拍攝，足見此機在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">Eric Schaal</span><span style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">心目中是何等重要。</span></p>\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\n            tab-stops:119.25pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">大部份僅餘的黑漆<span lang=\"EN-US\">MP</span>都較為殘舊，此套<span lang=\"EN-US\">MP</span>連<span lang=\"EN-US\">LEICAVIT</span>及鏡頭成色可算為上上之選。<br>\n            經由<span lang=\"EN-US\">James Lager</span>檢閱。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">估價：<span lang=\"EN-US\">HK$3,000,000   </span>–<span lang=\"EN-US\"> HK$4,000,000</span></span></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:2;height:13.4pt\">\n            <td width=\"633\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:474.85pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\n            border-top:none;mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;\n            padding:0cm 1.4pt 0cm 1.4pt;height:13.4pt\">\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right:6.0pt;mso-para-margin-right:.5gd;\n            text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;mso-line-height-alt:0pt\"><b><u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\n            mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">Lot 82. </span></u></b><b><u><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\n            Tahoma;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">著名攝影師<span lang=\"EN-US\">Jay Maisel Leica MP</span>銀色連號相機<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></u></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right:6.0pt;mso-para-margin-right:.5gd;\n            text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;mso-line-height-alt:0pt\"><b><u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\n            mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">Serial no. MP-222 &amp;   MP-223, 1956-1957, B+/C+</span></u></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right:6.0pt;mso-para-margin-right:.5gd;\n            text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;mso-line-height-alt:0pt\"><img src=\"/public/content/img_contents/LOTNO_82_1.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"313\" style=\"text-align: center;\" alt=\"\"></p>\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right:6.0pt;mso-para-margin-right:.5gd;\n            text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;mso-line-height-alt:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">這對早期的連號銀色<span lang=\"EN-US\">MP(MP-222</span>及<span lang=\"EN-US\">MP-223)</span>是由當代美國著名攝影師<span lang=\"EN-US\">Jay Maisel</span>自<br>\n            <span lang=\"EN-US\">1957</span>年起一直所擁有，從相機的外觀品相可見，<span lang=\"EN-US\">Jay Maisel</span>對它們的喜愛及使用程度<br>\n            非淺。伴隨著這對<span lang=\"EN-US\">MP</span>拍品的還有兩幅<span lang=\"EN-US\">Jay Maisel</span>最為人熟悉的攝影作品，<span lang=\"EN-US\">Marilyn Monroe<br>\n            (</span>瑪麗蓮·夢露）及<span lang=\"EN-US\">Miles Davis(</span>邁爾斯·戴維斯<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>，這兩幅相片均有<span lang=\"EN-US\">Jay Maisel</span>的簽名，<br>\n            同時還連同一封由<span lang=\"EN-US\">Jay Maisel</span>發出的確認信，證明這對相連號相機為他本人所擁有。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right:6.0pt;mso-para-margin-right:.5gd;\n            text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;mso-line-height-alt:0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">MP</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">相機是徠卡除<span lang=\"EN-US\">M3</span>以外，另一傳奇的機型。產於<span lang=\"EN-US\">1956-1957</span>年間的<span lang=\"EN-US\">MP</span>，是當年徠卡<br>\n            為極少數專業記者及攝影師而製的，銀色<span lang=\"EN-US\">MP</span>只有<span lang=\"EN-US\">311</span>台，同時配有快速過片器，極為<br>\n            稀有。經過大半世紀的洗禮，本來已為數不多的<span lang=\"EN-US\">MP</span>被分散世界各地，並落入不同的收<br>\n            藏家手中，幾乎從未在拍賣會上有現身過相連號碼的<span lang=\"EN-US\">MP</span>相機；且此對連號的經典<span lang=\"EN-US\">MP<br>\n            </span>相機由著名美國攝影師所擁有，更具收藏價值。此對相機分別配有同期供<span lang=\"EN-US\">MP</span>使用的<br>\n            <span lang=\"EN-US\">Summicron-M 2/5cm</span>鏡頭<span lang=\"EN-US\">(#1474704)</span>以及<span lang=\"EN-US\">Summicron-M 2/5cm</span>鏡頭<span lang=\"EN-US\">(#1474914)</span>，<br>\n            連同鏡頭前蓋及<span lang=\"EN-US\">MP Leicavit</span>，操作正常。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\n            mso-line-height-alt:0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">估價：<span lang=\"EN-US\">HK$2,500,000 </span>–<span lang=\"EN-US\"> HK$3,800,000<span style=\"color:#464646\"></span></span></span></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:3;height:56.25pt\">\n            <td width=\"633\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:474.85pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\n            border-top:none;mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;\n            padding:0cm 1.4pt 0cm 1.4pt;height:56.25pt\">\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right:6.0pt;mso-para-margin-right:.5gd;\n            text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;mso-line-height-alt:0pt\"><b><u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\n            9.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\n            mso-font-kerning:0pt\">Lot 68. Leica </span></u></b><b><u><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\n            mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">第二台黑漆<span lang=\"EN-US\">M3</span>相機<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></u></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right:6.0pt;mso-para-margin-right:.5gd;\n            text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;mso-line-height-alt:0pt\"><b><u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\n            9.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\n            mso-font-kerning:0pt\">Serial no. 746572, 1955, B/B-</span></u></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right:6.0pt;mso-para-margin-right:.5gd;\n            text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;mso-line-height-alt:0pt\"><img src=\"/public/content/img_contents/LOTNO_68_1.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"379\" style=\"text-align: center;\" alt=\"\"></p>\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right:6.0pt;mso-para-margin-right:.5gd;\n            text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;mso-line-height-alt:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">本拍品是第二台生產的<span lang=\"EN-US\">M3</span>黑漆相機，也是目前市面上已出現的最早一台，機頂的前後位<br>\n            置各鑲有兩粒螺絲作固定用途。此特徵是惟有在該首批<span lang=\"EN-US\">M3</span>黑漆擁有的特徵，從沒出現於<br>\n            其他黑漆版<span lang=\"EN-US\">M3</span>上。通常在市面上的資料記載首批量產的黑漆<span lang=\"EN-US\">M3</span>機身號是由<span lang=\"EN-US\">959401</span>至<br>\n            <span lang=\"EN-US\">959500</span>，但此機機身號卻是更早的<span lang=\"EN-US\">746572</span>，本拍品這首<span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span>台特別訂製黑漆版<span lang=\"EN-US\">M3</span>中的第<br>\n            二台；出廠至今一直由一名美國專業攝影師所擁有。此拍品連同<span lang=\"EN-US\">Ottmar   Michaely</span>的鑑定<br>\n            書，證實此機為百分百原裝，並在六十年代送返紐約徠茲進行升級，使<span lang=\"EN-US\">LEICAVIT(</span>快速過<br>\n            片器<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>能用於此機，除此以外其餘仍保持當年原裝的出廠配置<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>特別是內部機械結構<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right:6.0pt;mso-para-margin-right:.5gd;\n            text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;mso-line-height-alt:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">此機連同三支黑漆版鏡頭<span lang=\"EN-US\"> : </span>分別是黑漆<span lang=\"EN-US\">Summilux-M 1.4/50mm</span>、<br>\n            黑漆<span lang=\"EN-US\">Summicron-M 2/5cm</span>及黑色<span lang=\"EN-US\">Summilux-M 1.4/35mm</span>鋼咀，首兩支卡口為罕見的<br>\n            黃銅，最後的一支是沒有帶眼鏡版本，十分罕有。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right:6.0pt;mso-para-margin-right:.5gd;\n            text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;mso-line-height-alt:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">首批訂製的黑漆<span lang=\"EN-US\">M3</span>數量罕有程度更甚於<span lang=\"EN-US\">MP Black Paint</span>，而且此機是第二台黑漆<span lang=\"EN-US\">M3</span>，<br>\n            也是目前市面上唯一擁有機頂前後共四顆螺絲的黑漆<span lang=\"EN-US\">M3</span>。本拍品同時經<span lang=\"EN-US\">Ottmar Michaely<br>\n            </span>及<span lang=\"EN-US\">Lars Netopil</span>鑑定。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right:6.0pt;mso-para-margin-right:.5gd;\n            text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;mso-line-height-alt:0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">估價：<span lang=\"EN-US\">HK$1,800,000 </span>–<span lang=\"EN-US\"> HK$2,800,000</span></span></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:4;height:56.25pt\">\n            <td width=\"633\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:474.85pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\n            border-top:none;mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;\n            padding:0cm 1.4pt 0cm 1.4pt;height:56.25pt\">\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right:6.0pt;mso-para-margin-right:.5gd;\n            text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;mso-line-height-alt:0pt\"><b><u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\n            9.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\n            mso-font-kerning:0pt\">Lot 195. Leica M6</span></u></b><b><u><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\n            mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">汶萊蘇丹壽辰鑽石黃金紀念套機<span lang=\"EN-US\"><br>\n            Serial no. 2283239 (HB039), 1996, Condition A +</span></span></u></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right:6.0pt;mso-para-margin-right:.5gd;\n            text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;mso-line-height-alt:0pt\"><img src=\"/public/content/img_contents/LOTNO_195_1.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"450\" alt=\"\"></p>\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right:6.0pt;mso-para-margin-right:.5gd;\n            text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;mso-line-height-alt:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">本拍品在外觀上已使人望之儼然，在機身及鏡頭上均鍍以<span lang=\"EN-US\">24K</span>黃金，黃金機身上鑲嵌了一<br>\n            枚珍奇奪目的美鑽，根據拍品中附有的<span lang=\"EN-US\">EGL</span>證書，此鑽石淨度達<span lang=\"EN-US\">VVS1</span>的<span lang=\"EN-US\">F</span>級。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><br>\n            </span>源於<span lang=\"EN-US\">1996</span>年為慶祝汶萊國王<span lang=\"EN-US\">50</span>歲壽辰，汶萊皇室向徠卡訂製<span lang=\"EN-US\">125</span>套的<span lang=\"EN-US\">24K</span>黃金鑽石套機。<br>\n            在<span lang=\"EN-US\">24K</span>鍍金機身上覆以高貴的紅色蜥蝪皮，機頂上刻有專屬號碼「<span lang=\"EN-US\">HB039</span>」；機背則刻有國<br>\n            王<span lang=\"EN-US\">50</span>壽辰的日期–「<span lang=\"EN-US\">15th July 1996</span>」及「<span lang=\"EN-US\">In Commemoration of The   50th Birthday of <br>\n            His Majesty Sultan</span>」字樣，完美演繹出皇室尊貴的氣魄。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><br>\n            </span>此機連同<span lang=\"EN-US\">24K</span>鍍金<span lang=\"EN-US\">Summilux-M 1.4/35mm   ASPH (#3751039)</span>，鏡頭上亦刻有專屬號碼<br>\n            「<span lang=\"EN-US\">HB039-125</span>」，並配有精緻的鍍金鏡頭前蓋。附設機身蓋、鏡頭後蓋、背帶