 text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;mso-line-height-alt:0pt\"><img src=\"/public/content/img_contents/LOTNO_176_1.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"352\" style=\"color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\" alt=\"\"></p>\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right:6.0pt;mso-para-margin-right:.5gd;\n            text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;mso-line-height-alt:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">根據<span lang=\"EN-US\">James Lager Vol.I p.50</span>和<span lang=\"EN-US\">p.55</span>敘述，徠卡於<span lang=\"EN-US\">1942-1943</span>年間專門為德國軍隊生產<br>\n            了大約<span lang=\"EN-US\">130</span>台<span lang=\"EN-US\">250GG</span>相機，它們獨有的特徵包括快門布簾印有「<span lang=\"EN-US\">K</span>」字及帶滾珠軸承<br>\n            <span lang=\"EN-US\">(Kugellager)</span>，而且機底配有馬達介面，可提高在戰場上的拍攝速度。根據徠卡工廠紀<br>\n            錄，此對<span lang=\"EN-US\">250GG</span>在二次大戰期間被盜，之後這對相機輾轉流散於世界各地，成為了不同<br>\n            收藏者的手中掌珍，超過半世紀，竟能再度成雙出現於本拍賣會，堪稱奇蹟。本相連號<br>\n            帶<span lang=\"EN-US\">K</span>字布簾的<span lang=\"EN-US\">250GG</span>相機中，分別配有<span lang=\"EN-US\">Summar   2/5cm(#442081)</span>及<br>\n            <span lang=\"EN-US\">Summar 2/5cm (#468684)</span>鏡頭，連皮套、菲林匣及鏡頭前蓋。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right:6.0pt;mso-para-margin-right:.5gd;\n            text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;mso-line-height-alt:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">另外此拍品更包括一件估計是<span lang=\"EN-US\">1940</span>年德軍向徠卡訂造的，可用在<span lang=\"EN-US\">250 Reporter</span>的負片<br>\n            放大觀片配件“<span lang=\"EN-US\">NAKUL</span>”，此觀片器帶有手柄，兩端各有一個承托長膠片的金屬筒，觀<br>\n            片器有<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>倍放大效果，用刻有「<span lang=\"EN-US\">Betrachtungslupe fuer   Kleinbild-Aufnahme</span>」的灰色木<br>\n  