nfont-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">全場總成交價約<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>千<span lang=\"EN-US\">280</span>萬港元<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></u></b></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\nline-height:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">　<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>仕宏拍賣<span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span>年秋季相機拍賣會於<span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span>日<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>星期日<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>假香港君悅酒店圓滿結束，徠卡<span lang=\"EN-US\">(Leica)</span>資深書籍作家<span lang=\"EN-US\">Mr. Paul Henry</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\nfont-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\nArial\">Van Hasbroeck</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">，著名徠卡<span lang=\"EN-US\">(Leica)</span>相機鑑定專家<span lang=\"EN-US\">Mr. Lars Netopil</span>及日本<span lang=\"EN-US\">ICS</span>協會<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\n&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">Imported Camera&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\nArial\">Society of </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\n&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">Japan)</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\n&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">主席<span lang=\"EN-US\">Mr. Hosokawa</span>皆專程來港出席拍賣會。本次拍賣會推出<span lang=\"EN-US\">308</span>件拍賣品，總成交額約<span lang=\"EN-US\">3,280</span>萬港元<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>含佣金<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>，於國際稀有﹑古董相機拍賣會中先拔頭籌。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; text-indent: 21.3pt; line-height: 15.6pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><img src=\"/public/content/img_contents/20131117_auction.jpg\" width=\"650\" height=\"340\" longdesc=\"http://www.lhauction.com.hk/admin/fckeditor/editor/undefined\" style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; text-indent: 0px;\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 21.3pt; line-height: 15.6pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\nArial\">仕宏拍賣有限公司總裁周先生表示：「本屆拍賣會業績斐然，拍賣品除吸引香港及中國買家關注外，更有來自亞洲其他地區，如日本﹑台灣等的藏家踴躍競拍，足以顯示大中華地區對稀有、經典相機及相關配件需求的不斷增長，能媲美歐美地區的相機拍賣市場。同時我們觀察到來自歐美海外的買家比第一屆增長<span lang=\"EN-US\">20%-30%</span>，預計在<span lang=\"EN-US\">2014</span>年春季拍賣會中將會吸引更多藏家委託拍賣他們的藏品。」<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; text-indent: 15pt; line-height: 16.8pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><img src=\"/public/content/img_contents/20131117_bidding_lot_74.jpg\" alt=\"bidding_lot_74\" width=\"650\" height=\"354\" longdesc=\"http://www.lhauction.com.hk/admin/fckeditor/editor/undefined\" style=\"font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; text-indent: 0px;\"></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 15pt; line-height: 16.8pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\nArial\">拍賣會中最高成交價的拍品為全球只有<span lang=\"EN-US\">138</span>部的徠卡<span lang=\"EN-US\">MP</span>黑漆相機連同期黑漆<span lang=\"EN-US\">Summicron-M 2/5cm</span