         </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td width=\"671\" valign=\"top\">\n            <p><b>有關James L.   Lager </b></p>\n            <div>於20世紀70年James L. Lager已於美國Leitz技術部工作，之後更參與相機器材銷售。至今已編著八部關於經典LEICA的書籍，是為國際著名研究LEICA的權威。</div>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>					</div>', 'admin', 'admin', '1371830400', '1523329929', null, '1', null, null, '/public/pdf/content/1523009469.pdf', '/public/pdf/content/1523009468.pdf', null), ('47', 'Leica Camera Auction Organized by L&H Auction', '仕宏拍賣首屆相機拍賣會', '3', '', '<div class=\"pcontent\">\n<p>&nbsp;<b>ess Release[FOR IMMEDIATE RELEASE]</b>&nbsp;<b>14 June 2013</b></p>\n<p><b> <br>\n</b></p>\n<div align=\"center\"><b><u>Leica Camera Auction Organized by L&amp;H Auction</u></b></div>\n<div align=\"center\"><b><u>&nbsp;</u></b></div>\n<p>We are delighted to bring you the L&amp;H Photographica Auction, the first time ever held in Hong Kong. As Leica collectors like you, you can’t definitely miss it out! Consulted by James L. Larger, the renowned Leica researcher and historian. There are around 200 pieces of rare vintage camera, and auction will be taken place on 22 June 2013 at Grand Hyatt Hotel Hong Kong.</p>\n<div><b><u>&nbsp;</u></b></div>\n<p>The highlighted piece by auction is the custom-made M6 Platinum Sultan of Brunei Birthday Edition with diamond embedded, on celebrating his golden birthday in 1995. It is very rare to find one with serial number HB-000, and comes with an unique Summilux-M 1.4/35mm numbered #375200, #HB000-125. This camera was once one of the collections of Leica Museum in Solms, complete set shipped with its original lenscap and wooden box, and left the museum since 2003. The estimated value is ranged from HK$2,200,000 to HK$2,800,000.</p>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<p>In this auction, Leica is the majority while other prestige brands will be offered. Around 200 classic cameras, lenses and related accessories are available for your bid. Making bid can be in person, by mail, by fax, e-mail and by telephone. L&amp;H Auction also accept giving bid on web, <a href=\"http://www.liveauctioneers.com/\">www.liveauctioneers.com</a></p>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<p>Preview will be held in Hong Kong in mid-June, exhibited the exceptional items from Leitz/Leica that are valued at HK$20,000,000. Catalogue will be sent on request, please send your personal data including name, phone number, email/address to <a href=\"mailto:auction@lh-hk.com\">auction@lh-hk.com</a> or call 852-3168 2188 or visit <a href=\"http://www.lhauction.com.hk/\">www.lhauction.com.hk</a> for further details.</p>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><b><u>Preview</u></b></div>\n<p>Date:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 18 - 21 June 2013 (11:00 a.m. - 7:00 p.m.)<br>\n22 June 2013 (9:00 a.m. - 12:00 p.m.)</p>\n<p>Venue:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Shop No. 9-11, 10/F, Windsor House, 311 Gloucester Road, Causeway Bay, Hong Kong</p>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><b><u>Auction</u></b></div>\n<div>Date:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 22 June 2013 (1:00 p.m. - 5:00 p.m.)</div>\n<div>Venue:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Grand Hyatt Hong Kong, Library and Lounge, 1 Harbour Road, Wan Chai, Hong Kong</div>\n<p>Registration:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Please send the personal information including name, phone number and e-mail to <a href=\"file:///C:/Users/LH/Desktop/auction@lh-hk.com\">auction@lh-hk.com</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div><b>Description </b><b>and Picture</b><b> of Selected Items</b></div>\n<table border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"674\">\n    <tbody>\n        <tr>\n            <td width=\"54\" valign=\"top\">\n            <div align=\"center\"><b>Lot</b><b> No.</b></div>\n            </td>\n         