Birthday   Edition with Diamond</u></b><br>\n            To celebrate 50th birthday of his majesty, Sultan   Brunei ordered the special limited edition from Leica in 1995. There were 150 pieces made with diamond on the top plate and come with   Summilux-M 1.4/50mm, special number started with   HB001. But more particularly, the camera in this auction carried with serial   no. HB-000 which is the first unit of this batch, and the lens is Summilux-M   1.4/35mm (#375200, #HB000-125). This camera was property of the Leica Museum in Solms, leave in Leica museum up to 2003. Extremely rare, comes with   lens cap.</p>\n            </td>\n            <td width=\"76\">\n            <div align=\"center\">HKD</div>\n            <div align=\"center\">$2,800,000</div>\n            </td>\n            <td width=\"232\">\n            <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"/public/content/img_contents/135.png\" width=\"230\" height=\"175\" alt=\"\"></p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td width=\"54\">\n            <div align=\"center\">146.</div>\n            </td>\n            <td width=\"312\">\n            <p><b><u>146. MP Edition</u></b><b><u>《</u></b><b><u>60 Years PRC</u></b><b><u>》</u></b><b><u>with Summilux-M 1.4/50mm ASPH Gold Plated<br>\n            </u></b>In commemoration the 60th Anniversary of the People‘s   Republic of China Leica has produced 24 carat gold-plated MP with Summilux-M 1.4/50mm ASPH #4073525, body covered with red calf skin, only   61 units made, each bears a mark between 1949 and 2009,   engraved “ 中華人民共和國萬歲” on the top.   This commemorative number is 1987, complete with full packing in brand new   condition. Extremely rare.</p>\n            </td>\n            <td width=\"76\">\n            <div align=\"center\">HKD</div>\n            <div align=\"center\">$400,000</div>\n            </td>\n            <td width=\"232\">\n            <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"/public/content/img_contents/146.png\" width=\"230\" height=\"183\" alt=\"\"></p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td width=\"54\">\n            <div align=\"center\">147.</div>\n            </td>\n            <td width=\"312\">\n            <p><b><u>M9-P Edition Hermès with Three Lenses Kit<br>\n            </u></b>Leica M9-P Edition Hermès comes with Summicron-M 2/28mm ASPH, Noctilux-M 0.95/50mm   ASPH &amp; Summicron-M 2/90mm ASPH; only   100 units produced. The commemorative number is 52/100 , comes with Hermès   camera bag and strap, hood, full packing and brand new condition.</p>\n            </td>\n            <td width=\"76\">\n            <p align=\"center\">HKD<br>\n            $480,000</p>\n            </td>\n            <td width=\"232\">\n            <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"/public/content/img_contents/147.png\" width=\"230\" height=\"139\" alt=\"\"></p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<p>High quality pictures can be downloaded from our ftp:</p>\n<div><a href=\"http://www.lhauction.com.hk/pr_download/Auction\">http://www.lhauction.com.hk/pr_download/Auction</a></div>\n<p>Login ID:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; lhhk</p>\n<div>Password:&nbsp;&nbsp; lhhk</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<p>For press enquiry, please contact:</p>\n<div><b>L&amp;H Auction Co. Ltd (</b><b>仕宏拍賣有限公司</b><b>)</b></div>\n<div>Ms Stephanie Kwok&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Tel：(852) 3168 2192&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; E-mail：stephanie@lh-hk.com</div>\n<div>Ms Annie Liu&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 　 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 　Tel：(852) 3168 2192 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; E-mail：annieliu@lh-hk.com</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<table border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"671\">\n    <tbody>\n        <tr>\n            <td width=\"671\" valign=\"top\">\n            <div><b>About </b><b>L&amp;H Auction</b></div>\n            <p>L&amp;H Auction Co.   Ltd. specializes in sourcing the exceptional cameras and lenses from all over   the world. James L. Lager, Leica researcher   and historian serves as the consultant.</p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td width=\"671\" valign=\"top\">\n            <div><b>About </b><b>James L. Lager </b></div>\n            <p>In 1971 he joined   the Leica Technical Center of E. Leitz, Inc. Rockleigh, N.J. He has engaged   in the retail sector of the photo industry since 1975. Internationally recognized as an authority on   Leica cameras and systems, renowned author of important publications   of Leica.</p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table>					</div>\n', '<div class=\"pcontent\">\n<p>&nbsp;<b>新聞稿 [即時發佈]</b>&nbsp;<b>30.05.2013</b></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><b><u>仕宏拍賣首屆相機拍賣會</u></b></p>\n<div>　　仕宏拍賣第一屆拍賣會將於2013年6月22日(星期六)假香港君悅酒店舉行，本次拍賣會邀請到LEICA歷史學家James L. Lager作為顧問，打造香港專業相機拍賣會。仕宏拍賣於全球搜羅稀有古董相機，價值連城，拍賣會當日全數推出，供全球買家競投。</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b>&nbsp;&nbsp; 當中亮點包括一部史上最高貴華麗的紀念機，1995年為慶祝汶萊國王50歲生日，特別罕有地向德國徠卡訂製極少數量帶鑽石的M6 鉑金紀念機，此款紀念機徠卡公司沒有對外發行，是供汶萊國王送給特別貴賓用。機身特別編號由＂ HB-001 ＂開始，而本次拍賣會中的此套紀念機編號為＂HB-000＂，並且是當中唯一一部連Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPH (#375200, #HB000-125) 鏡頭的紀念機。此機是徠卡公司只供汶萊國王看的樣機，屬徠卡公司的財產，之後一直存放在徠卡博物館，直到2003 年才流出市面。此套紀念機是史上最為高貴華麗的紀念機，全球僅此一套。此套機連鏡頭蓋及精美木盒。現時估計約值2,200,000至2,800,000港元。</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>拍賣品中更有數部非常罕有的LEICA機型，包括全球只有一百套的M7 <a href=\"http://www.hermes.com/\">Hermès</a>橙色套機﹑MP鈦金屬機﹑於1956年為瑞典軍隊生產的IIIf 黑漆軍機﹑1960年瑞典皇家軍隊訂製，機身及鏡頭刻有三皇冠標誌的皇家軍機等。</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>　　除上述拍賣品外，拍賣品中亦有多枚LEICA古董鏡頭。當中包括一枚徠茲加拿大工廠 (Leitz of Midland Canada) 為美軍於1970年越南戰爭而設計的長焦鏡。該款鏡頭僅生產54枚，本次的拍賣鏡頭最後第二枝，鏡身上有“303-0053”字樣。此款鏡頭至今從未對外發佈，鏡頭經歷戰爭洗禮，僅存市場上的可能不足一半，極為罕見。現時估計約值100,000至150,000港元。</div>\n<p><b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </b></p>\n<div>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 是次公開拍賣會以LEICA為主，同時亦搜羅多款其他品牌的經典產品，合共約拍賣二百件經典相機、鏡頭及相關配件，全屬價值連城的珍藏品。除親臨拍賣會場，可通過信件﹑傳真﹑電子郵件及電話競標；仕宏拍賣亦開放網上同步競投，網上競投者可透過<a href=\"http://www.liveauctioneers.com/\">www.liveauctioneers.com</a>進行登記。</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>　　部份拍賣品將於6月中於香港進行拍賣會預展，展出大量珍貴古董相機，價值將近二千萬港元，歡迎公眾參觀。如欲索取是次拍賣品目錄，可連同姓名及聯絡電話電郵至<a href=\"mailto:auction@lh-hk.com\">auction@lh-hk.com</a>，或致電852-3168 2188查詢有關詳情。</div>\n<div>網站：<a href=\"http://www.lhauction.com.hk/\">www.lhauction.com.hk</a></div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><b><u>L&amp;H AUCTION</u></b><b><u>香港預展詳情</u></b></div>\n<p>&nbsp;日期：2013年6月18日－6月21日(上午11時至晚上7時)<br>\n&nbsp;　2013年6月22日 (上午 9時至中午12時)&nbsp;<br>\n&nbsp; 地點：香港銅鑼灣告士打道311號皇室堡10樓09-11室</p>\n<p><b><u>L&amp;H AUCTION</u></b><b><u>仕宏拍賣會詳情</u></b><br>\n&nbsp; 日期：2013年6月22日(下午1時至下午5時)<br>\n&nbsp; 地點：香港灣仔港灣道一號君悅酒店(Library &amp; Lounge)<br>\n&nbsp; 登記：請將個人資料包括姓名、聯絡電話及電郵發送至<a href=\"file://diskstation/Project/L&amp;H_Auction/Auction1_June2013/2013_1/PR/Press%20Release/auction@lh-hk.com\">auction@lh-hk.com</a></p>\n<div><b>部份拍賣品簡介及圖片</b></div>\n<table border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"669\">\n    <tbody>\n        <tr>\n            <td width=\"64\" valign=\"top\">\n            <div><b>拍賣編號</b></div>\n            </td>\n            <td width=\"293\" valign=\"top\">\n            <div><b>簡介</b></div>\n            </td>\n            <td width=\"66\" valign=\"top\">\n            <div align=\"center\"><b>估價</b></div>\n            </td>\n            <td width=\"246\" valign=\"top\">\n            <div align=\"center\"><b>圖片</b></div>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td width=\"64\">\n            <div align=\"center\">18.</div>\n            </td>\n            <td width=\"293\">\n            <p><b><u>LEICA IIIf </u></b><b><u>銀</u></b><b><u>色原型機(測驗機)<br>\n            </u></b>LEICA 為生產IIIg而準備的原型機機身，有別於正常機型，閃燈同步及加大的取景框。其機身背後的測距及取景結合成為同一個目鏡，比正常較大，而閃燈同步插口則移到右邊。</p>\n            </td>\n            <td width=\"66\">\n            <div align=\"center\">80萬港元</div>\n            </td>\n            <td width=\"246\">\n            <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"/public/content/img_contents/1.png\" alt=\"\"><